ail%20and%20explain%20his%20reason%20for%20opposing%20the%20CAA%20to%20the%20general%20public.%20In%20politics%2C%20it's%20your%20responsibility%20to%20justify%20your%20decisions.%20If%20the%20CAA%20is%20a%20decision%20by%20my%20government%2C%20I%20have%20to%20explain%20my%20party's%20position%2C%20the%20government's%20decision%20and%20why%20it%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20nation.%20Similarly%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20explain%20his%20opposition%20to%20the%20legislation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20had%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20promulgation%20of%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act.%20The%20Congress%20alleged%20that%20this%20was%20a%20controversial%20law%20because%20citizenship%20is%20never%20based%20on%20religion%2C%20it%20goes%20against%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20was%20only%20indulging%20in%20politics%20of%20lies%20as%20the%20CAA%20had%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20manifesto%20for%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20was%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20in%202019%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20opposition%20parties%20including%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mamata%20or%20Kejriwal%20are%20indulging%20in%20'jhooth%20ki%20rajneeti'%20(politics%20of%20lies)%20so%20the%20question%20of%20timing%20does%20not%20arise.%20BJP%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20in%20its%202019%20manifesto%20that%20it%20will%20bring%20CAA%20and%20provide%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20refugees%20(from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan).%20BJP%20has%20a%20clear%20agenda%20and%20under%20that%20promise%2C%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20in%202019.%20It%20got%20delayed%20due%20to%20Covid.%20BJP%20had%20cleared%20its%20agenda%20well%20before%20the%20party%20got%20its%20mandate%20in%20the%20polls%26quot%3B%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRules%20are%20now%20a%20formality.%20There%20is%20no%20question%20of%20timing%2C%20political%20gain%20or%20loss.%20Now%2C%20the%20Opposition%20wants%20to%20consolidate%20their%20vote%20bank%20by%20doing%20appeasement%20politics.%20I%20want%20to%20request%20them%20that%20they%20have%20been%20exposed.%20CAA%20is%20the%20law%20for%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20I%20have%20reiterated%20nearly%2041%20times%20in%20four%20years%20that%20it%20will%20become%20a%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20said%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20question%20of%20political%20gain%20as%20the%20main%20aim%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20to%20provide%20rights%20and%20justice%20to%20persecuted%20minorities%20coming%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opposition%20had%20even%20raised%20questions%20on%20surgical%20strike%20and%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20linked%20it%20with%20political%20gain.%20So%20should%20we%20not%20take%20stern%20steps%20against%20terrorism%3F%20We%20have%20been%20saying%20since%201950%20that%20we%20will%20withdraw%20Article%20370%26quot%3B%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20on%20March%2011%20notified%20CAA%20Rules%2C%202024%2C%20removing%20legal%20barriers%20to%20rehabilitation%20and%20citizenship%20to%20such%20persons%2C%20and%20will%20give%20a%20dignified%20life%20to%20refugees%20who%20have%20suffered%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAA%20aims%20to%20provide%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20-%20including%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Parsis%2C%20and%20Christians%20-%20who%20migrated%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%20and%20arrived%20in%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710392700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fmvqmvip8_rahul-gandhi_625x300_07_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-should-publicly-explain-his-opposition-to-caa-amit-shah-5235111%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20dismissed%20former%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20party's%20criticism%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20rules%20of%20which%20were%20notified%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-should-publicly-explain-his-opposition-to-caa-amit-shah-5235111%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-should-publicly-explain-his-opposition-to-caa-amit-shah-5235111%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-should-publicly-explain-his-opposition-to-caa-amit-shah-5235111%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seeking%20Citizenship%20Under%20CAA%2C%20But%20No%20Documents%3F%20Amit%20Shah's%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20today%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcitizenship-amendment-act-how-to-apply-for-citizenship-under-new-law-key-questions-answered-5222785%5C%22%3ECitizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20or%20CAA%3C%2Fa%3E%20currently%20does%20not%20have%20a%20provision%20for%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20who%20do%20not%20possess%20the%20required%20documents%2C%20but%20said%20the%20government%20will%20soon%20work%20on%20a%20way%20out%20for%20such%20refugees.%20The%20Centre%20on%20Monday%20notified%20the%20CAA%20to%20reduce%20the%20qualification%20period%20of%20application%20for%20citizenship%20from%2011%20to%205%20years%20for%20persecuted%20migrants%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%20who%20came%20to%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20applying%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20under%20the%20scheme%20will%20need%20to%20furnish%20two%20documents%20-%20one%20to%20prove%20they%20came%20from%20the%20eligible%20countries%2C%20and%20another%20to%20establish%20that%20they%20entered%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-not-anti-muslim-amit-shah-slams-opposition-attacks-on-citizenship-law-5235283%5C%22%3EAmit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20according%20to%20government%20estimates%2085%25%20of%20the%20people%20in%20India%20who%20are%20seeking%20to%20apply%20under%20the%20scheme%20have%20the%20required%20documents.%20But%20the%20government%20will%20soon%20find%20an%20alternative%20for%20those%20who%20do%20not%20have%20any%20documents%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20find%20a%20way%20for%20those%20who%20do%20not%20have%20documents%20but%20those%20who%20have%20the%20documents%20constitute%20more%20than%2085%25.%20There%20is%20no%20time%20limit%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20can%20take%20time%20to%20apply%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20will%20call%20you%20for%20an%20interview%20as%20per%20the%20time%20available%20to%20you.%20The%20government%20will%20call%20you%20for%20the%20audit%20of%20the%20document%20and%20a%20face-to-face%20interview%20will%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20how%20the%20process%20will%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3D