quot%3BI%20have%20spoken%20on%20CAA%20at%20least%2041%20times%20on%20different%20platforms%20and%20spoken%20in%20detail%20that%20the%20minorities%20of%20the%20country%20need%20not%20be%20afraid%20because%20it%20has%20no%20provision%20to%20take%20back%20the%20rights%20of%20any%20citizen%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%2C%20he%20said%2C%20aims%20to%20give%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants%2C%20including%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Parsis%2C%20and%20Christians%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20who%20arrived%20in%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%2C%20he%20said%2C%20have%20the%20right%20to%20apply%20for%20citizenship%20in%20India%20as%20per%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20but%20this%20law%20is%20meant%20for%20persecuted%20minorities%20from%20these%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20government%20may%20rethink%20its%20decision%20to%20implement%20the%20CAA%20if%20protests%20begin%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCAA%20will%20never%20be%20rolled%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20tore%20into%20the%20Opposition%20for%20targeting%20its%20decision%20to%20implement%20the%20law.%20Asked%20about%20a%20Congress%20leader's%20remark%20stating%20that%20they%20would%20roll%20back%20CAA%20when%20they%20come%20to%20power%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20INDI%20alliance%20knows%20that%20it%20will%20not%20come%20to%20power.%20CAA%20has%20been%20brought%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20has%20brought%20it.%20It%20is%20impossible%20to%20repeal%20it.%20We%20will%20spread%20awareness%20across%20the%20nation%20so%20that%20those%20who%20want%20to%20repeal%20it%20do%20not%20get%20a%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dismissed%20the%20criticism%20that%20CAA%20is%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20law%20does%20not%20violate%20Article%2014.%20There%20is%20a%20clear%2C%20reasonable%20classification%20here.%20This%20is%20a%20law%20for%20those%20who%2C%20due%20to%20partition%2C%20remained%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Bangladesh%20and%20were%20facing%20religious%20persecution%20and%20decided%20to%20come%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20Opposition's%20attack%20on%20the%20timing%20of%20implementing%20the%20law%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20or%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20are%20indulging%20in%20jhooth%20ki%20rajneeti%20(politics%20of%20lies)%2C%20so%20the%20question%20of%20timing%20does%20not%20arise.%20BJP%20made%20it%20clear%20in%20its%202019%20manifesto%20that%20it%20will%20bring%20CAA%20and%20provide%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20refugees%20(from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan).%20BJP%20has%20a%20clear%20agenda%20and%20under%20that%20promise%2C%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20in%202019.%20It%20got%20delayed%20due%20to%20Covid.%20BJP%20had%20cleared%20its%20agenda%20well%20before%20the%20party%20got%20its%20mandate%20in%20the%20polls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20notifying%20the%20rules%20was%20a%20formality%2C%20so%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20timing%20or%20political%20gain%20or%20loss.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20the%20Opposition%20wants%20to%20consolidate%20their%20vote%20bank%20by%20doing%20appeasement%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Minister%20said%20the%20Opposition%20had%20raised%20questions%20on%202016%20surgical%20strikes%20and%20the%20revocation%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status.%20%26quot%3BSo%20should%20we%20not%20take%20stern%20steps%20against%20terrorism%3F%20We%20have%20been%20saying%20since%201950%20that%20we%20will%20withdraw%20Article%20370%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20see%20this%20law%20in%20isolation.%20On%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20our%20country%20was%20partitioned%20into%20three%20parts.%20This%20is%20the%20background.%20Bharatiya%20Jan%20Sangh%20and%20BJP%20were%20always%20against%20the%20Partition.%20We%20never%20wanted%20the%20country%20to%20be%20partitioned%20based%20on%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20when%20the%20country%20was%20partitioned%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%2C%20minorities%20faced%20persecution%2C%20they%20were%20being%20converted%2C%20women%20in%20the%20minority%20section%20were%20being%20tortured%20and%20came%20to%20India.%20They%20came%20to%20our%20refuge%3B%20don't%20they%20have%20a%20right%20to%20get%20our%20citizenship%3F%20Even%20Congress%20leaders%20during%20the%20partition%20in%20their%20speeches%20said%20that%20those%20minorities%20should%20stay%20wherever%20they%20are%20due%20to%20the%20widespread%20bloodshed%20and%20they%20will%20be%20welcomed%20later%20in%20our%20country.%20Then%20they%20started%20doing%20vote%20bank%20politics%20for%20appeasement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%2C%20who%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20citizenship%20of%20minorities%20would%20be%20taken%20away%20through%20CAA%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20requesting%20Mamata%20ji%2C%20there%20are%20several%20platforms%20to%20do%20politics%2C%20but%20please%20don't%20harm%20Bengali%20Hindus%20coming%20from%20Bangladesh.%20I%20challenge%20her%20publicly%20to%20show%20one%20such%20clause%20that%20has%20the%20provision%20of%20taking%20away%20the%20citizenship%20of%20any%20Indian.%20Her%20intention%20is%20to%20create%20differences%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20to%20consolidate%20vote%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710390780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fb732cp28_amit-shah_625x300_14_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-not-anti-muslim-amit-shah-slams-opposition-attacks-on-citizenship-law-5235283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stressing%20that%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20is%20not%20against%20the%20Muslims%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20of%20resorting%20to%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20of%20lies%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-not-anti-muslim-amit-shah-slams-opposition-attacks-on-citizenship-law-5235283%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-not-anti-muslim-amit-shah-slams-opposition-attacks-on-citizenship-law-5235283%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-not-anti-muslim-amit-shah-slams-opposition-attacks-on-citizenship-law-5235283%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20%2480%20billion%20question%3A%20What%20next%20for%20small-cap%20stocks%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710390753000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108481538%2Cimgsize-36948.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fbse-sensex-nifty-small-cap-stocks-madcap-stocks-stock-market-fall%2Farticleshow%2F108481553.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20S%26amp%3BP%20BSE%20Small%20Cap%20Index%20has%20experienced%20a%20significant%20drop%2C%20declining%20over%2012%25%20from%20its%20peak%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Despite%20this%20downturn%2C%20many%20investors%20have%20seized%20the%20opportunity%20to%20purchase%20more%20shares%2C%20maintaining%20a%20positive%20outlook%20on%20Indian%20equities.%20This%20optimism%20is%20echoed%20by%20domestic%20institutional%20investors%2C%20including%20mutual%20funds%20and%20insurance%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Bloomberg%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fbse-sensex-nifty-small-cap-stocks-madcap-stocks-stock-market-fall%2Farticleshow%2F108481553.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20No%20Protest%20Against%20Rohingyas%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20Jabs%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20On%20CAA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20criticism%20made%20by%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20regarding%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20asserted%20that%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20supremo's%20outburst%20stemmed%20from%20his%20party's%20alleged%20exposure%20in%20corruption%20cases%20and%20said%20if%20he%20is%20concerned%20about%20national%20security%20that%20he%20must%20talk%20about%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20this%20week%20reiterated%20his%20earlier%20remarks%20on%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20stating%20that%20more%20migration%20will%20now%20take%20place%20than%20after%20independence.%20He%20further%20claimed%20that%20law%20and%20order%20will%20collapse%20and%20subsequently%20lead%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20thefts%2C%20robberies%2C%20and%20rapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20lost%20his%20temper%20after%20his%20party's%20alleged%20corruption%20got%20exposed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Kerjiwal)%20is%20unaware%20that%20all%20these%20people%20have%20already%20taken%20refuge%20in%20our%20country.%20They%20are%20living%20in%20India.%20Those%20who%20arrived%20in%20our%20country%20by%202014%20will%20get%20citizenship%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20he%20is%20concerned%2C%20why%20does%20he%20not%20talk%20about%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators%3F%20Why%20does%20he%20not%20protest%20against%20Rohingyas%3F%20It%20is%20because%20they%20are%20doing%20vote-bank%20politics.%20He%20will%20face%20a%20very%20tough%20time%20during%20elections%20in%20Delhi%20that%20is%20why%20he%20is%20doing%20vote-bank%20politics.%20Are%20Rohingyas%20and%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators%20not%20taking%20our%20jobs%3F%20He%20is%20just%20raising%20his%20voice%20against%20minorities%20of%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20and%20Parsis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20will%20have%20to%20face%20great%20difficulty%20in%20the%20Delhi%20elections.%20Are%20Rohingyas%20and%20Bangladeshi%20infiltrators%20not%20taking%20our%20jobs%3F%20He%20is%20just%20raising%20his%20voice%20against%20minorities%20of%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20and%20Parsis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20further%20said%20that%20leaders%20like%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20have%20no%20sympathy%20for%20those%20who%20came%20here%20after%20being%20persecuted%20in%20their%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20forgotten%20the%20background%20of%20the%20Partition.%20These%20refugees%20came%20here%20after%20leaving%20their%20property%20worth%20millions%20behind.%20Why%20won't%20we%20listen%20to%20their%20problems%3F%20They%20don't%20get%20jobs%20and%20education%20here.%20Why%20won't%20we%20express%20sympathy%20with%20them%3F%20It%20was%20not%20their%20decision%20to%20partition%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20the%20Congress%20which%20decided%20that%20and%20they%20promised%20them%20citizenship.%20Now%20they%20are%20backtracking%20on%20their%20promises%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2011%2C%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20notified%20rules%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20scheduled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAA%20aims%20to%20