and%20unnecessary%20verbal%20exchanges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fsome-of-them-cant-stomach-ipl-fees-of-indians-sunil-gavaskar-criticizes-englands-attitude-tying-it-to-lack-of-ipl-success%2Farticleshow%2F108479916.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CAA%20Should%20Be%20for%20All%20Persecuted%20People%20%E2%80%98Irrespective%20of%20Religion%E2%80%99%2C%20Says%20Taliban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F14090928%2FDj40h9qF_400x400.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20its%20first%20reaction%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Taliban%E2%80%99s%20head%20of%20political%20office%20in%20Doha%2C%20Suhail%20Shaheen%2C%20said%20that%20any%20such%20law%20should%20be%20for%20all%20%E2%80%9Cirrespective%20of%20religion%E2%80%9D%2C%20even%20as%20he%20denied%20that%20there%20was%20any%20persecution%20of%20minorities%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2011%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20notified%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20controversial%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act.%20Announcing%20the%20rules%2C%20Indian%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20it%20will%20%E2%80%9Cenable%20minorities%20persecuted%20on%20religious%20grounds%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20to%20acquire%20citizenship%20in%20our%20nation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stated%20objective%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20parliament%20in%20December%202019%2C%20is%20to%20accelerate%20the%20process%20of%20granting%20citizenship%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jains%20and%20Christians%20purportedly%20fleeing%20persecution%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslim-majority%20neighbours%20%E2%80%93%20namely%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%20However%2C%20the%20cut-off%20date%20for%20refugees%20to%20arrive%20in%20India%20to%20qualify%20under%20the%20CAA%20is%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Taliban%20spokesperson%20and%20head%20of%20the%20political%20office%20in%20Doha%20Suhail%20Shaheen%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20should%20apply%20to%20all%20whether%20they%20are%20Muslims%2C%20Hindus%20or%20Sikhs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20for%20clarification%20on%20whether%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20CAA%2C%20Shaheen%20affirmed%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20it%20should%20be%20for%20all%20who%20are%20persecuted%20in%20their%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Shaheen%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Taliban%E2%80%99s%20designated%20Permanent%20Representative%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20persecution%20of%20Sikhs%20and%20Hindus%20in%20Taliban-ruled%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20minorities%20like%20Sikh%20and%20Hindus%20are%20not%20persecuted%20in%20Afghanistan%3B%20they%20have%20freedom%20of%20performing%20their%20rituals%20and%20have%20the%20same%20right%20in%20the%20sight%20of%20the%20law%20as%20I%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaheen%20additionally%20expressed%20his%20hope%20for%20equal%20treatment%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20also%20minority%20in%20India%20i.e.%20Muslims%2C%20are%20not%20persecuted%20as%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%20are%20not%20persecuted%20in%20Afghanistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22SC%20Receives%20Three%20Petitions%20a%20Day%20After%20Govt%20Notifies%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20Rules%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-receives-three-petitions-a-day-after-govt-notifies-citizenship-amendment-act-rules%5C%22%3ESC%20Receives%20Three%20Petitions%20a%20Day%20After%20Govt%20Notifies%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20Rules%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20is%20being%20implemented%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20has%20improved%20ties%20with%20the%20Taliban%20government%20in%20Kabul%2C%20despite%20not%20according%20it%20full%20diplomatic%20recognition%20in%20line%20with%20the%20international%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20now%20a%20team%20of%20diplomats%20in%20the%20Afghan%20capital%2C%20with%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20officials%20regularly%20meeting%20with%20Taliban%20government%20officials.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffor-first-time-in-taliban-era-indian-technicians-return-to-inspect-265-million-dam-in-afghanistan%5C%22%3Erecently%20also%20sent%20a%20technical%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20look%20at%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20India-Afghanistan%20friendship%20dam%20at%20Herat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghan%20embassy%20in%20New%20Delhi%20is%20also%20now%20manned%20by%20Afghan%20diplomats%20who%20are%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20central%20foreign%20ministry%20in%20Kabul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Taliban%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%20has%20cooled%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20(TTP)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20behind%20a%20series%20of%20terror%20attacks%20by%20Islamabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20CAA%20was%20approved%20by%20parliament%20in%20December%202019%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Afghanistan%20was%20still%20at%20the%20helm.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20to%20clarify%20that%20the%20allegations%20of%20persecution%20was%20not%20being%20made%20against%20the%20post-2001%20Afghanistan%20government%2C%20but%20specifically%20against%20the%20Taliban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20Afghanistan%2C%20you%20see%20we%20have%20and%20especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20statement%20which%20came%20out%20from%20their%20side%20especially%20when%20we%20spoke%20about%20the%20minorities%2C%20we%20said%20that%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20that%20religious%20persecution%20is%20taking%20place%20under%20the%20present%2C%20the%20current%20government%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F32248%2FTranscript_of_Weekly_Media_Briefing_by_Official_Spokesperson_December_19_2019%5C%22%3Esaid%20MEA%20spokesperson%20at%20the%20weekly%20briefing%20of%20December%2019%2C%202019%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20explained%20that%20%E2%80%9Cduring%20the%20previous%20Mujahideen%20and%20Taliban%20regimes%2C%20religious%20minorities%20were%20deliberately%20victimised%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%20in%202001%20and%20we%20are%20all%20aware%20of%20that%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20Taliban%20issued%20a%20call%20for%20minorities%20to%20%E2%80%9Cconvert%20to%20Islam%20or%20leave%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20also%20reiterated%20the%20clean%20chit%20to%20the%20Islamic%20Republic.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20aware%20that%20the%20current%20government%20has%20substantially%20addressed%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20minorities%20as%20per%20their%20constitutional%20provisions%20and%20laws.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20link%20between%20the%20Taliban%20and%20the%20persecution%20of%20minorities%20was%20also%20reiterated%20by%20Indian%20government%20ministers%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20return%20of%20the%20insurgent%20group%20to%20Kabul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20week%20after%20the%20Taliban%20returned%20to%20power%2C%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20plane%20airlifting%20Indians%20from%20Kabul%20also%20brought%20back%2024%20Afghan%20Sikhs%20and%20Hindus.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20minister%20of%20urban%20affairs%20and%20petroleum%20Hardeep%20Puri%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhardeepspuri%2Fstatus%2F1429356598686715904%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Crecent%20developments%20in%20our%20volatile%20neighbourhood%20%26amp%3B%20the%20way%20Sikhs%20%26amp%3B%20Hindus%20are%20going%20through%20a%20harrowing%20time%20are%20precisely%20why%20it%20was%20necessary%20to%20enact%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20over%20300%20Afghan%20Sikhs%20and%20Hindus%20arrived%20in%20India%20after%20the%20Taliban%20takeover.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20them%20would%20qualify%20for%20Indian%20citizenship%20under%20the%20amended%20law%2C%20and%20most%20of%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FOLOlt%5C%22%3Edeparted%20for%20foreign%20shores%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Unlike%20in%20India%20where%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20financial%20means%20to%20survive%2C%20refugees%20who%20are%20rehabilitated%20in%20western%20countries%20often%20get%20funds%20till%20they%20get%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Home%20Ministry%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Positive%20Narrative%E2%80%99%20on%20CAA%20is%20Full%20of%20Lies%2C%20Half-Truths%20and%20Really%20Bad%20Drafting%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministrys-positive-narrative-on-caa-is-full-of-lies-half-truths-and-really-bad-drafting%5C%22%3EHome%20Ministry%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Positive%20Narrative%E2%80%99%20on%20CAA%20is%20Full%20of%20Lies%2C%20Half-Truths%20and%20Really%20Bad%20Drafting%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20former%20Afghan%20Sikh%20lawmakers%20who%20fled%20Kabul%20have%20also%20left%20India%20%E2%80%93%20Narendra%20Singh%20Khalsa%20is%20in%20Canada%2C%20while%20Anarkali%20Kaur%20Honaryar%20took%20refuge%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Taliban%20government%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafghanistan-news-sikhs-in-kabul-assured-of-safety-sikhs-in-kabul-gurudwara-in-video-shared-by-taliban-2513867%5C%22%3Eheld%20a%20series%20of%20a%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Hindu%20and%20Sikh%20leaders%20over%20several%20months%20after%20they%20came%20to%20power%20to%20assure%20them%20of%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meetings%20also%20took%20place%20after%20the%20insurgent%20Islamic%20State%20in%20Khorasan%20Province%20(ISKP)%20took%20responsibility%20for%20attacks%20on%20a%20gurudwara%20in%20Kabul%20in%202022.%20Incidentally%2C%20the%20MEA%20expedited%20the%20pending%20visas%20for%20over%20100%20Afghan%20Sikhs%20after%20the%202022%20gurudwara%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20Taliban%20asserted%20that%20Afghan%20Sikhs%20and%20Hindus%20should%20return%20to%20their%20homeland%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wionews.com%2Fsouth-asia%2Ftaliban-urges-minorities-to-return-claims-security-situation-in-afghanistan-has-been-addressed-500734%5C%22%3Esecurity%20situation%20had%20been%20resolved%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Guljeet%20Singh%2C%20a%20social%20worker%20who%20is%20involved%20with%20the%20Afghan%20Sikh%20community%20in%20Delhi%2C%20there%20were%20only%20two%20families%20left%20after%20the%20Taliban%20takeover%2C%20who%20were%20also%20preparing%20to%20leave%20the%20country.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20that%20there%20are%20thousands%20of%20pending%20applications%20for%20citizenship%20from%20Afghan%20Sikhs%20and%20Hindus%20over%20the%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20around%2050%20men%20have%20returned%20to%20earn%20their%20living%20from%20their%20shops%20and%20properties%20in%20Kabul%20and%20Jalalabad.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20their%20assets.%20But%20they%20are%20staying%20together%20in%20a%20community%20centre%20or%20gurudwara%20for%20safety%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20the%20Afghan%20Sikhs%20and%20Hindus%20felt%20danger%20from%20the%20Taliban%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20group%20was%20not%20tar