reedom%20of%20expression%20and%20an%20encroachment%20of%20peoples%E2%80%99%20everyday%20lives%2C%20especially%20if%20it%20is%20done%20to%20shut%20down%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEgypt%E2%80%99s%202011%20revolution%20and%20the%20failed%20Turkish%20military%20coup%20of%202016%20are%20prime%20examples%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F11456%2Finternet-freedom-worldwide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternet%20shutdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0employed%20in%20this%20way.%20In%20India%20%E2%80%93%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F6071%2Finternet-freedom-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecountry%20that%20cuts%20internet%20access%20the%20most%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20shutdowns%20have%20in%20the%20past%20clustered%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20they%20have%20been%20used%20during%20protests%20(and%20preemptively%20when%20protests%20were%20expected)%2C%20but%20also%20during%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20ethnic%20tensions%20in%20Manipur%20state%20led%20to%20most%20targeted%20shutdowns%20employed%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%202023%20Indian%20internet%20blockages%20and%20shutdowns%20affected%20around%2059%20million%20people%20for%20a%20total%20of%20almost%208%2C000%20hours%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.top10vpn.com%2Fresearch%2Fcost-of-internet-shutdowns%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20highest%20in%20the%20world%20when%20combined%20according%20to%20Top10VPN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ethiopia%2C%20Myanmar%20and%20Iran%2C%20the%20suppression%20of%20dissent%2C%20protest%20and%20in%20one%20instant%20the%20Orthodox%20church%2C%20have%20caused%20almost%20equally%20long%20user%20hours%20of%20internet%20blocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20world%2C%20internet%20shut