t%20Looms%20As%20New%20Research%20Reveals%20Widespread%20Impact%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBird%20flu%2C%20a%20disease%20known%20as%20H5N1%2C%20has%20been%20gaining%20attention%20lately%20as%20scientists%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20conspiracy%20theorists%20gear%20up%20for%20potential%20pandemics.%20However%2C%20a%20warning%20from%20a%20scientist%20suggests%20that%20another%20pandemic%20might%20already%20be%20underway%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Metro.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Diana%20Bell%2C%20a%20conservation%20biology%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20East%20Anglia%2C%20points%20out%20that%20bird%20flu%20has%20been%20spreading%20rapidly%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20emerging%20in%20domestic%20geese%20in%20China%20in%201997%2C%20the%20disease%20has%20since%20extended%20its%20reach%20across%20continents%2C%20affecting%20various%20non-avian%20species%20besides%20birds%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F03%2F13%2Fexpert-reveals-shocking-numbers-behind-pandemic-affecting-millions-20457011%2F%3Fito%3Darticle.app.share.top.whatsapp%5C%22%3Enews%20outlet.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwwwnc.cdc.gov%2Feid%2Farticle%2F30%2F3%2F23-1098_article%5C%22%3ERecent%20research%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehighlighted%20by%20Dr%20Bell%20reveals%20that%20since%202020%2C%2026%20countries%20have%20reported%20numerous%20mammal%20species%20falling%20victim%20to%20the%20virus.%20Even%20polar%20bears%20and%20dolphins%20have%20been%20affected%2C%20with%20alarming%20numbers%20of%20deaths%20observed%20in%20various%20animal%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20cases%20have%20also%20been%20reported%2C%20with%20882%20cases%20of%20bird%20flu%20across%2023%20countries%20in%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20worrying%20fatality%20rate%20of%2052%25.%20Poultry-to-human%20infections%2C%20notably%20prevalent%20in%20certain%20Asian%20countries%2C%20raise%20concerns%20about%20t