0mud-houses%20there.%20In%20Pure%20Bariyarpur%20the%20Dalit%20neighbourhood%20was%20separated%20from%20the%20village%20to%20create%20a%20new%20village%2C%20Jogapur.%20While%20Pure%20Baryarpur%20has%20amenities%2C%20many%20Dalits%20in%20Jogapur%20have%20no%20taps.%20The%20water%20in%20handpumps%20is%20so%20polluted%20that%20one%20can%20see%20it%20with%20bare%20eyes.%20Some%20have%20got%20houses%20under%20the%20Indira%20Awas%20Yojana.%20In%20Kakrahiya%2C%20which%20is%20an%20exception%2C%20villagers%20say%20their%20condition%20was%20better%20even%20before%20Modi%20adopted%20them.%20Many%20have%20taps%2C%20water%20and%20pakka%20houses.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20saw%20inaugural%20stones%20of%C2%A0%20a%20school%20and%20road%20by%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%20village.%20Villagers%20say%20that%20is%20because%20the%20village%20is%20dominated%20by%20%E2%80%9Cupper%20castes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131804%2FSJ4.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131804%2FSJ4.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131804%2FSJ4-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701444%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20washing%20utensils%20with%20stale%20water%20in%20Parampur%20village.%20Photo%3A%20Srishti%20Jaswal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanshu%2C%20an%20associate%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jnu.ac.in%2Fcontent%2Fhimanshu2%5C%22%3E%20professor%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%E2%80%99s%20Centre%20for%20Economic%20Studies%20and%20Planning%20said%20there%20are%20many%20issues%20in%20the%20design%20of%20policies.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20subsidies%20given%20for%20these%20policies%20are%20hardly%20enough%20and%20local%20corruption%20makes%20it%20even%20more%20difficult%20to%20make%20a%20change%20on%20ground.%20The%20toilet%20is%20a%20good%20example.%20They%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20non-functional%20because%20with%20such%20little%20money%2C%20hardly%20any%20good%20toilets%20can%20be%20made.%20Similarly%20in%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20the%20subsidy%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20be%20able%20to%20build%20a%20proper%20house.%20Then%20there%20is%20convergence%20between%20various%20programmes%2C%20for%20instance%20people%20are%20given%20a%20toilet%20without%20housing%20or%20people%20are%20given%20housing%20without%20tap%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20406px)%2085vw%2C%20406px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13134054%2FIMG_2860.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BJP%20promises%20performance%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22406%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13134054%2FIMG_2860.jpg%20874w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13134054%2FIMG_2860-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13134054%2FIMG_2860-746x1024.jpg%20746w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701457%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22557%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20corroborated%20on%20the%20ground%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%20While%20Lal%20Dhar%20in%20Jayapur%20has%20a%20toilet%20with%20a%20broken%20door%2C%20he%20has%20no%20house.%20Similarly%2C%20Mohit%20Chauhan%20from%20Domri%20village%20does%20not%20have%20a%20house%20but%20he%20has%20a%20tap%20and%20a%20toilet.%20Karma%20Devi%20from%20Nagepur%20has%20no%20house%2C%20no