%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202023%2C%20Lim%20opened%20up%20a%20stall%20serving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-hawker-stall-nasi-lemak-best-food-changi-photos-review-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enasi%20lemak%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20Malay%20coconut%20rice%20dish%20served%20with%20side%20dishes%20like%20fried%20chicken%2C%20dried%20anchovies%2C%20otah%2C%20or%20spiced%20fish%20cake%2C%20and%20sambal%2C%20a%20sweet%2C%20spicy%20chili%20sauce.%20The%20small%20hawker%20center%20is%20located%20in%20a%20bustling%20neighborhood%20in%20eastern%20Singapore%2C%20surrounded%20by%20blocks%20of%20public%20housing%20and%20wet%20markets.%20It%20was%20a%20world%20away%20from%20the%20glitzy%2C%20towering%20skyscrapers%20and%20million-dollar%20shophouses%20that%20surrounded%20Zen%20downtown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELim%20named%20her%20stall%20%26quot%3BSo%20Lemak%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20flavor%20descriptor%20unique%20to%20Malay%20cuisine.%20According%20to%20local%20food%20historian%20Khir%20Johari%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fweek-asia%2Flifestyle-culture%2Farticle%2F3159270%2Fwhat-makes-singaporean-malay-food-unique-mee-rebus-nasi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elemak%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20richness%20and%20creaminess%20of%20coconut%20milk%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20key%20ingredient%20in%20nasi%20lemak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22shanice%20lim%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eec5cf90413ab8e1db47aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221538%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELim's%20hawker%20stall%20in%20Bedok%20is%20popular%20among%20people%20of%20all%20ages.%3Cp%3EMarielle%20Descalsota%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ETook%20a%20risk%20with%20a%20demanding%20trade%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHawker%20centers%20are%20the%20heart%20of%20Singapore's%20local%20food%20culture.%20There%20are%20%3Ca%20hr