is%20interview.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESahil%20Gaba%20was%20four%20years%20out%20of%20graduate%20school%20and%20working%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Amazon%20when%20a%20recruiter%20contacted%20him%20to%20interview%20at%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaba%20had%20interviewed%20at%20Google%20twice%20before%2C%20in%202016%20and%202018%20respectively.%20Neither%20round%20of%20interviews%20turned%20into%20an%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20been%20struggling%20to%20get%20a%20job%20for%20a%20long%20time%20at%20that%20point%20and%20had%20faced%20hundreds%20of%20rejections%20by%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaba%20told%20Business%20Insider%20about%20his%20two%20interview%20experiences.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20another%20rejection%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20he%20wasn't%20worried%20about%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20kind%20of%20stopped%20caring%20about%20the%20results%20of%20the%20interviews%20because%20I%20had%20taken%20and%20failed%20so%20many%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaba%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20way%2C%20it's%20quite%20liberating%20when%20you%20go%20in%20with%20a%20mindset%20that%20you've%20seen%20it%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20eight%20rounds%20of%20interviews%2C%20he%20got%20a%20job%20offer%20with%20Google%20in%202021%20as%20a%20software%20engineer.%20Here's%20what%20his%20years%20of%20interview%20experience%20taught%20him%20about%20big%20tech%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuild%20interview%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coding%20rounds%20of%20big%20tech%20interviews%2C%20there%20are%20two%20parts%20to%20solving%20a%20question%20%E2%80%94%20coming%20up%20with%20the%20solution%2C%20and%20writing%20the%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20was%20new%2C%20I%20would%20be%20under%20more%20pressure%20while%20writing%20the%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20extra%20years%20of%20experience%20took%20away%20part%20of%20the%20stress%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNow%20writing%20the%20code%20is%20not%20the%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20I%20could%20come%20up%20with%20the%20solution%2C%20the%20writing%20part%20was%20straightforward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20time%20he%20interviewed%20at%20Google%2C%20Gaba%20switched%20his%20programming%20language%20of%20choice%20from%20Java%20to%20Python%20in%20interviews%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20move%20that's%20still%20debated%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20sped%20up%20my%20coding%20ability%20in%20the%20interviews%20a%20lot%20because%20it's%20very%20easy%20to%20think%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20Java.%20%26quot%3BEven%20to%20this%20day%2C%20I%20don't%20use%20Python%20at%20work%2C%20but%20let's%20say%20if%20I%20have%20to%20interview%20tomorrow%2C%20I'll%20be%20using%20Python.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterviewing%20in%20low-pressure%20situations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInterviewing%20while%20he%20had%20a%20job%20he%20was%20happy%20with%20took%20away%20some%20of%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20process%2C%20Gaba%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20time%20he%20interviewed%20at%20Google%2C%20Gaba%20said%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20an%20immediate%20exit%20from%20his%20job%20at%20the%20time%2C%20which%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20he%20liked%20his%20job%2C%20which%20helped%20him%20stay%20calm%20at%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20enjoying%20working%20with%20my%20coworkers%20at%20Amazon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20really%20have%20any%20problem%20staying%20back%20either.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuying%20negotiating%20power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20third%20round%20of%20interviews%20at%20Google%2C%20Gaba%20followed%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20set%20up%20interviews%20at%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Uber%20close%20to%20each%20other%20so%20that%20offers%20%E2%80%94%20if%20he%20got%20them%20%E2%80%94%20would%20roll%20in%20around%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would%20give%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bslightly%20upper%20hand%20in%20negotiation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that%20helped%20me%20be%20able%20to%20negotiate%20my%20salary%20with%20all%20the%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelying%20less%20on%20referrals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGaba%20said%20he%20used%20to%20rely%20heavily%20on%20referrals%20to%20apply%20for%20jobs%20in%20big%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20had%20exhausted%20his%20network%20and%20still%20hadn't%20landed%20a%20job%2C%20he%20started%20applying%20to%20companies%20directly%20through%20their%20job%20portals.%20When%20he%20applied%20to%20Amazon%2C%20he%20applied%20to%20not%20one%2C%20but%20to%2010%20or%2015%20positions%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20strategy%20is%20that%20one%20recruiter%20has%20multiple%20openings%3A%20%26quot%3BEssentially%20you're%20not%20applying%20for%20a%20job%2C%20you're%20applying%20for%20a%20recruiter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-interview-big-tech-coding-skills-sofware-engineering-sahil-gaba-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710376322000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f122056080194819ff3c41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-interview-big-tech-coding-skills-sofware-engineering-sahil-gaba-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20took%20Sahil%20Gaba%20hundreds%20of%20job%20rejections%20and%20years%20of%20coding%20experience%20to%20finally%20land%20a%20job%20at%20Google%20on%20his%20t