0Campaign%20Slugfest%20Intensifies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20needled%20%26quot%3Bloser%26quot%3B%20Donald%20Trump%20Wednesday%2C%20in%20his%20first%20battleground%20campaign%20stop%20since%20the%20two%20rivals%20secured%20their%20parties'%20nominations%20for%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rancorous%20elections%20in%20US%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20supporters%20in%20Milwaukee%20in%20the%20crucial%20swing%20state%20of%20Wisconsin%2C%20the%20Democrat%20also%20blasted%20his%20hard-right%20Republican%20nemesis%20for%20describing%20immigrants%20as%20%26quot%3Bvermin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20to%20the%20campaign%20trail%20came%20a%20day%20after%20incumbent%20Biden%2C%2081%2C%20and%20Trump%2C%2077%2C%20both%20won%20enough%20delegates%20to%20clinch%20their%20parties'%20nominations%20for%20a%20rematch%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20you%20helped%20me%20in%202020%20and%20we%20made%20sure%20he%20was%20a%20loser.%20And%20we're%20going%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20happens%20again%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20local%20supporters%20and%20volunteers%20in%20Milwaukee%20--%20the%20same%20city%20where%20Trump%20and%20his%20party%20will%20hold%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20taken%20to%20repeatedly%20calling%20Trump%20a%20loser%2C%20knowing%20it%20rankles%20the%20defeated%20former%20president%2C%20who%20still%20refuses%20to%20acknowledge%20he%20lost%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWisconsin%20and%20Michigan%2C%20which%20Biden%20will%20visit%20on%20Thursday%2C%20were%20among%20the%20crucial%20states%20he%20flipped%20from%20Trump%20in%20their%202020%20showdown%20and%20needs%20to%20win%20again%20to%20secure%20a%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20took%20on%20Trump%20over%20immigration%2C%20a%20key%20issue%20in%20the%20election%20with%20the%20Republican%20resorting%20to%20increasingly