es%20for%20meetings%20and%20parties%20at%20events%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-cannes-lions-are-brands-brave-enough-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECannes%20Lions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-disney-streamers-plan-big-advertising-sales-push-ces-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Electronics%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20larger-than-life%20Kassan%20always%20prominently%20center%20stage%2C%20hobnobbing%20with%20CEOs%20and%20celebrities.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-hollywood-agency-uta-bought-medialink-consultancy-cannes-lions-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUTA%20acquired%20the%20company%20for%20%24125%20million%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20marrying%20its%20roster%20of%20entertainment%20talent%20with%20MediaLink's%20network%20of%20advertising%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20less%20than%20three%20years%20on%2C%20the%20partnership%20is%20headed%20for%20a%20messy%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20UTA%20spokesperson%20said%20Tuesday%20Kassan%20was%20%26quot%3Bterminated%20for%20cause%26quot%3B%20on%20March%207%20%26quot%3Bfollowing%20a%20thorough%20and%20exhaustive%20third-party%20investigation%20into%20misappropriation%20of%20company%20funds.%26quot%3B%20The%20talent%20agency%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20him%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Superior%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20alleging%20constructive%20fraud%2C%20and%20breaches%20of%20a%20partner%20services%20agreement%2C%20fiduciary%20duty%2C%20and%20duty%20of%20loyalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKassan's%20attorney%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20he%20had%20filed%20his%20own%20claim%20with%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Judicial%20Arbitration%20and%20Mediation%20Services%2C%20naming%20UTA%20and%20its%20CEO%20Jeremy%20Zimmer%20among%20the%20defendants%20and%20alleging%20they%20breached%20his%20contract%20by%20c