%3BNo%20conflict%2C%20no%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20Kassan's%20motto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Madison%20Avenue%20is%20buzzing%20about%20whether%20the%20MediaLink%20mafia%20can%20continue%20without%20its%20Godfather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHalf%20the%20value%20just%20walked%20out%20the%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jon%20Miller%2C%20a%20veteran%20media%20executive%20who%20serves%20as%20CEO%20of%20Integrated%20Media%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20digital%20media%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20end%20of%20MediaLink%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20executive%20at%20a%20competitor%20firm%20to%20MediaLink%2C%20which%20expects%20to%20pick%20up%20business%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20UTA%20turmoil.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20ever%20was%20a%20business%20that%20was%20completely%20tied%20to%20its%20CEO%2C%20it's%20that.%26quot%3B%20The%20exec%2C%20like%20many%20people%20contacted%20for%20this%20story%2C%20asked%20for%20anonymity%20to%20speak%20freely%20on%20a%20sensitive%20situation%20or%20because%20they%20weren't%20authorized%20to%20discuss%20it%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20UTA%20spokesperson%20said%20MediaLink%20has%20a%20strong%20executive%20team%20in%20place%20that%20continues%20to%20carry%20the%20business%20forward.%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20not%20be%20any%20disruption%20for%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UTA%20spokesperson%20said.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20MediaLink%20directed%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20to%20UTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKassan's%20attorney%2C%20Sanford%20Michelman%20of%20Michelman%20and%20Robinson%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20his%20client's%20first%20priority%20is%20the%20success%20and%20continued%20growth%20of%20MediaLink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20looks%20forward%20to%20ensuring%20its%20continued%20success%20in%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222337%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Kassan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f9c6a876f5b310011724914%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Kassan.%3Cp%3EEthan%20Miller%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETalent%20agencies%20are%20retrenching%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUTA's%20acquisition%20of%20MediaLink%20was%20one%20example%20of%20a%20long%20trend%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-like-pg-and-delta-are-using-hollywood-talent-agencies-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etalent%20agencies%20branching%20out%20to%20advertising%20services%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20it%20was%20Endeavor's%20WME%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbusiness-news%2Fendeavor-sells-stake-ad-agency-droga5-1199386%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuying%20a%2049%25%20stake%20in%20Droga5%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%20was%20later%20unloaded%20to%20consulting%20giant%20Accenture).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20buying%20MediaLink%2C%20UTA%20already%20had%20a%20marketing%20arm%2C%20led%20by%20Julian%20Jacobs%20and%20David%20Anderson%2C%20which%20connects%20brands%20to%20Hollywood%3B%20it%20recently%20brokered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-deal-gm-product-placement-ads-electric-vehicles-shows-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeal%20that%20put%20General%20Motors%20cars%20in%20Netflix%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance.%20UTA%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Futa-acquires-juv-consulting-gen-z-1235927795%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20acquired%20JUV%20Consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20agency%20that%20helps%20marketers%20reach%20Gen%20Z.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20always%20the%20idea%20that%20if%20you%20have%20the%20connection%20to%20culture%2C%20you%20can%20extract%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20from%20Madison%20Avenue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20former%20creative%20agency%20CEO.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20there%20are%20signs%20that%20the%20agencies%20are%20retrenching%2C%20however.%20WME%20is%20expected%20to%20sell%20non-core%20parts%20of%20its%20business%20after%20parent%20Endeavor%20said%20last%20fall%20that%20it%20was%20evaluating%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20alternatives%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20assets.%20And%20the%20talent%20agencies%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2021%2F06%2Fcaa-sells-majority-stake-wiip-korean-studio-jtbc-1234767146%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexited%20the%20content%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20resolve%20a%20dispute%20with%20the%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20falling%20out%20with%20Kassan%2C%20UTA%20may%20think%20twice%20about%20buying%20another%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20will%20run%20MediaLink%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20and%20ad%20industry%20will%20be%20watching%20to%20see%20what%2C%20if%20any%2C%20leadership%20changes%20UTA%20makes%20at%20MediaLink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKassan%20is%2073%20and%20was%20facing%20questions%20about%20his%20succession%20plans%20before%20this%20latest%20blow-up.%20A%20prior%20obvious%20natural%20successor%2C%20Kassan's%20longtime%20right%20hand%2C%20Wenda%20Harris%20Millard%2C%20left%20in%202022.%20People%20familiar%20with%20the%20company%20were%20hard-pressed%20to%20come%20up%20with%20names%20of%20top%20lieutenants%20whose%20industry%20stature%20came%20close%20to%20matching%20Kassan's.%20And%20the%20rift%20with%20UTA%20could%20complicate%20its%20ability%20to%20bring%20in%20outside%20talent%20to%20run%20it%2C%20should%20it%20try%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20client%20noted%20that%20Kassan%20had%20built%20a%20strong%20bench%20of%20talent%20at%20MediaLink%2C%20and%20a%20former%20MediaLink%20executive%20said%20that%20while%20Kassan%20was%20a%20driving%20force%20behind%20the%20company%20winning%20new%20business%2C%20he%20wasn't%20involved%20in%20most%20of%20the%20projects%20it%20works%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what's%20next%20for%20Kassan%2C%20speculation%20has%20run%20the%20gamut%2C%20with%20people%20imagining%20variously%20Kassan%20starting%20over%20on%20his%20own%2C%20settling%20with%20UTA%2C%20or%20buying%20his%20firm%20back.%20There's%20also%20conjecture%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20breakup%20between%20him%20and%20UTA%20head%20Zimmer%2C%20and%20whether%20there%20will%20be%20more%20juicy%20details%20to%20learn%20about%20Kassan's%20alleged%20spending%20and%20the%20MediaLink%20acquisition%20agreement%20beyond%20what%20has%20already%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKassan%20has%20a%20loyal%20following%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20imagine%20people%20giving%20him%20another%20chance%2C%20as%20they%20have%20done%20in%20the%20past.%20In%201999%2C%20he%20was%20fired%20by%20Western%20Initiative%20Media%20Worldwide%2C%20part%20of%20ad%20holding%20company%20Interpublic%20Group%2C%20after%20he%20sued%20the%20media%20buying%20company%20for%20%2463.5%20million%2C%20alleging%20breach%20of%20contract%20and%20defamation%20of%20character.%20The%20suit%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finterpublicgroup.gcs-web.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Finterpublic-and-michael-kassan-settle-lawsuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettled%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20in%201995%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Farchives%2Fla-xpm-1999-aug-17-fi-884-story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20was%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20practicing%20law%20in%20California%20after%20a%20conviction%20for%20grand%20theft%20by%20embezzlement.%20The%20charge%20was%20later%20reduced%20to%20a%20misdemeanor%20and%20expunged%20from%20his%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt'd%20be%20easier%20for%20him%20to%20start%20MediaLink%202.0%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lou%20Paskalis%2C%20a%20former%20Bank%20of%20America%20marketer%20and%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20AJL%20Advisory.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20us%20are%20going%20to%20just%20move%20from%20MediaLink%20to%20whatever%20Michael's%20new%20company%20is%2C%20because%20you're%20buying%20Michael%20Kassan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%20ad%20industry%20schmoozefest%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMediaLink%20grew%20out%20of%20a%20time%20when%20mistrust%20between%20agencies%20and%20marketers%20was%20running%20high%2C%20and%20the%20media%20landscape%20was%20growing%20more%20complicated%20with%20the%20entry%20of%20tech%20giants.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20business%20of%20building%20community%20in%20the%20ad%20industry%20has%20attracted%20new%20players%20like%20Marc%20Sternberg's%20Brand%20Innovators%20and%20Pttow%2C%20but%20they%20haven't%20come%20close%20to%20supplanting%20MediaLink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20companies%20have%20only%20gotten%20more%20powerful%2C%20and%20now%20AI%20is%20threatening%20to%20disrupt%20media%20buyers'%20and%20sellers'%20businesses%20even%20further.%20There%20still%20may%20be%20a%20place%20for%20connectors%20like%20Kassan.%20But%20agencies%20in%20particular%20are%20also%20frustrated%20about%20their%20reliance%20on%20MediaLink%2C%20especially%20because%20participating%20in%20the%20media%20agency%20reviews%20that%20MediaLink%20oversees%20comes%20at%20a%20high%20cost.%20One%20industry%20veteran%20said%20they%20saw%20Kassan's%20exit%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20change%20how%20ad%20industry%20consultants%20operate%20and%20charge%20for%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKassan's%20departure%20may%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end%20of%20the%20advertising%20industry%20schmoozefest.%20At%20the%20center%20of%20the%20dispute%20between%20UTA%20and%20Kassan%20is%20the%20MediaLink%20founder's%20%24950%2C000%20annual%20expense%20account.%20Cannes%20Lions%2C%20where%20MediaLink%20is%20omnipresent%2C%20is%20the%20ultimate%20industry%20tentpole%20event%2C%20where%20deals%20are%20signed%20on%20yachts%20in%20the%20opulent%20setting%20of%20the%20French%20Riviera.%20MediaLink%20parties%20attracted%20big-name%20%E2%80%94%20and%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20performers%2C%20from%20Lady%20Gaga%20to%20Elton%20John%20and%20Mariah%20Carey.%20(Kassan%20was%20notably%20absent%20from%20South%20by%20Southwest%20in%20Austin%20this%20month%2C%20where%20MediaLink%20hosted%20a%20client%20dinner%20with%20former%20NFL%20quarterback%20Tom%20Brady.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20else%20in%20the%20industry%20has%20the%20convening%20power%20of%20Michael%20Kassan%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20advertising%20industry%20veteran%20Rob%20Norman%2C%20the%20former%20global%20chief%20digital%20officer%20of%20WPP's%20GroupM.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20pull%20that%20bolt%20out%2C%20does%20the%20rest%20of%20it%20fall%20over%3F%20Then%20does%20it%20still%20matter%20to%20UTA%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmessy-michael-kassan-split-with-uta-puts-medialink-future-in-question-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710365681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f1fff36080194819ff881d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmessy-michael-kassan-split-with-uta-puts-medialink-future-in-question-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22News%20of%20a%20legal%20battle%20between%20Kassan%20and%20talent%20giant%20UTA%20has%20the%20ad%20world%20speculating%20about%20whether%20his%20firm%2C%20MediaLink%2C%20can%20go%20on%20without%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly%2CLucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmessy-michael-kassan-split-with-uta-puts-medialink-future-in-question-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Calculating%20Your%20Rent%20Budget%3A%20A%20Step-by-Step%20Guide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-rent-can-i-afford%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20answer%20readers'%20investing%20questions%20and%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting-rating-methodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20how%20we%20assess%20investing%20products%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Paid%20non-client%20promotion%3A%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20we%20receive%20a%20commission%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20opinions%20are%20always%20our%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20walks%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bfor%20rent%26quot%3B%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cbbe9494aa8ee8e84ad787%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHow%20much%20rent%20you%20can%20afford%20depends%20on%20how%20much%20money%20you%20bring%20home.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FPaul%20Sakuma%2C%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20general%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20that%20you%20should%20aim%20to%20spend%20no%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20your%20gross%20income%20on%20rent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20a%20better%20way%20to%20find%20out%20how%20much%20rent%20you%20can%20afford%20is%20to%20look%20at%20your%20overall%20budget%20and%20your%20individual%20needs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGetting%20a%20roommate%20or%20moving%20to%20a%20different%20neighborhood%20can%20help%20if%20you're%20struggling%20to%20afford%20rent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20typical%20household%20spends%20a%20hefty%20chunk%20of%20their%20earnings%20on%20three%20things%3A%20housing%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20median%20US%20renter%20spends%20about%2030%25%20of%20their%20gross%20income%20on%20rent%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Flibrary%2Fstories%2F2023%2F03%2Flow-income-renters-spent-larger-share-of-income-on-rent.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20US%20Census%20Bureau.%20But%20almost%20half%20of%20renters%20spend%20more%20than%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20the%20magic%20number%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20calculating%20rent%20affordability%3F%20Here's%20how%20to%20determine%20how%20much%20rent%20you%20can%20afford%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20much%20rent%20can%20I%20afford%3F%5C%22%3EHow%20much%20rent%20can%20I%20afford%3F%20The%2030%25%20rule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20spend%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20your%20income%20on%20rent%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Development%20considers%20you%20to%20be%20cost-burdened.%20If%20you%20spend%20more%20than%2050%25%2C%20you're%20severely%20cost-burdened.%20Being%20cost-burdened%20makes%20it%20much%20harder%20for%20individuals%20to%20afford%20other%20necessities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20often%20recommend%20that%20renters%20use%2030%25%20as%20a%20benchmark%20for%20how%20much%20they%20should%20spend%20on%20rent.%20But%20like%20any%20financial%20rule%20of%20thumb%2C%20it's%20not%20always%20right%20for%20every%20person's%20individual%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20many%20renters%20live%20in%20high-cost%20areas%20where%20spending%2030%25%20or%20less%20of%20their%20monthly%20income%20on%20rent%20is%20nearly%20impossible%20without%20an%20unusually%20high%20income.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20New%20York%20City%2C%20where%20the%20median%20monthly%20rent%20is%20%241%2C714%2C%20and%20the%20median%20income%20for%20an%20individual%20is%20%2448%2C066%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fquickfacts%2Ffact%2Ftable%2Fnewyorkcitynewyork%2CUS%2FPST045223%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20income%20equates%20to%20%244%2C006%20a%20month.%20To%20meet%20the%2030%25%20threshold%2C%20this%20person%20would%20need%20to%20spend%20around%20%241%2C202%20or%20less%20on%20rent%20%E2%80%94%20but%20instead%2C%20they're%20spending%20almost%2043%25%20on%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20can%20see%2C%20the%2030%25%20rule%20isn't%20always%20helpful%20for%20people%20in%20high-cost%20areas.%20Or%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20larger%20income%20or%20live%20in%20a%20low-cost%20area%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20wise%20to%20spend%20the%20full%2030%25%20on%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%2030%25%20rule%20can%20be%20a%20good%20starting%20point%20to%20give%20you%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20a%20reasonable%20amount%20to%20spend%20on%20rent%20might%20look%20like.%20Here's%20how%20to%20calculate%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EUsing%20the%2030%25%20rule%20to%20determine%20your%20rent%20payment%20capacity%3A%20A%20step-by-step%20guide%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDetermining%20affordable%20rent%20for%20your%20budget%20requires%20a%20bit%20of%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Find%20your%20gross%20monthly%20pay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20you%20earn%20each%20month%20before%20taxes.%20You%20can%20look%20at%20your%20paystubs%20to%20see%20what%20your%20gross%20pay%20is%2C%20or%20you%20can%20calculate%20it%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20paid%20a%20salary%2C%20take%20your%20annual%20salary%20and%20divide%20it%20by%2012.%20If%20you're%20paid%20hourly%2C%20multiply%20your%20hourly%20rate%20by%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20you%20work%20each%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Multiply%20your%20gross%20monthly%20pay%20by%2030%25%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20amount%20you%20earn%20before%20taxes%20each%20month%20and%20multiply%20it%20by%200.30.%20This%20is%20the%20maximum%20amount%20you%20should%20spend%20on%20rent%20each%20month%2C%20according%20to%20the%2030%25%20rule.%20This%20includes%20both%20the%20rent%20you%20pay%20each%20month%20as%20well%20as%20any%20utilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20See%20how%20this%20fits%20into%20your%20overall%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverybody%20has%20different%20needs%2C%20wants%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsavings-goals%5C%22%3Esavings%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20three%20things%20make%20up%20your%20budget%2C%20and%20because%20they're%20so%20individual%2C%20it's%20up%20to%20you%20to%20determine%20how%20to%20allocate%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%2030%25%20rule%20isn't%20suitable%20for%20you%20because%20rent%20is%20expensive%20in%20your%20city%2C%20you're%20likely%20going%20to%20need%20to%20pare%20back%20in%20other%20areas%20of%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-budget%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20room.%20Or%2C%20if%20you're%20saving%20aggressively%20for%20retirement%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20look%20for%20cheaper%20rental%20units%20so%20you%20can%20spend%20less%20of%20your%20income%20on%20housing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20having%20trouble%20figuring%20out%20how%20much%20you%20should%20spend%20overall%20each%20month%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%3Ebudgeting%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20make%20the%20process%20a%20bit%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Determining%20affordable%20rent%20for%20your%20budget%5C%22%3EDetermining%20affordable%20rent%20for%20your%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20experts%20recommend%20using%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2F50-30-20-rule%5C%22%3E50%2F30%2F20%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20set%20your%20budget%2C%20and%20this%20rule%20could%20help%20you%20with%20estimating%20suitable%20rent%20for%20your%20income%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20budgeting%20rule%2C%20you'll%20aim%20to%20spend%2050%25%20of%20your%20income%20on%20things%20you%20need%2C%2030%25%20on%20things%20you%20want%2C%20and%2020%25%20on%20debt%20payments%20and%20savings.%20This%20rule%20utilizes%20after-tax%20income%2C%20or%20your%20take-home%20pay%2C%20rather%20than%20your%20pre-tax%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bneeds%26quot%3B%20bucket%20includes%20housing%20costs%20as%20well%20as%20other%20things%20you%20need%20to%20survive%2C%20including%20food%20and%20transportation%20to%20get%20to%20work.%20To%20figure%20out%20how%20much%20of%20this%20category%20should%20be%20spent%20on%20rent%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20look%20at%20all%20of%20your%20necessary%20costs%20and%20see%20how%20much%20room%20you%20have%20for%20a%20monthly%20rent%20payment%20on%20top%20of%20those%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Rent%20budgeting%20tips%5C%22%3ERent%20budgeting%20tips%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20having%20trouble%20affording%20your%20rent%2C%20here%20are%20some%20things%20that%20might%20help%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrack%20your%20spending%20habits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20first%20step%20to%20finding%20more%20money%20in%20your%20budget%20is%20understanding%20where%20all%20your%20hard-earned%20money%20is%20going.%20You%20might%20find%20that%20you're%20paying%20for%20a%20subscription%20you%20no%20longer%20want%2C%20or%20that%20your%20occasional%20online%20shopping%20purchases%20are%20actually%20costing%20you%20more%20than%20you%20think.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESplit%20rent%20with%20a%20roommate.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Especially%20in%20high-cost%20areas%2C%20living%20with%20a%20roommate%20can%20substantially%20lower%20your%20rent%20burden%20and%20free%20up%20space%20in%20your%20budget%20for%20other%20things.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMove%20to%20a%20more%20affordable%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAverage%20rent%20prices%20can%20vary%20a%20lot%20from%20one%20town%20to%20the%20next%2C%20or%20even%20one%20neighborhood%20to%20the%20next.%20If%20you're%20able%20to%2C%20moving%20to%20a%20more%20affordable%20area%20can%20be%20a%20good%20way%20to%20save%20on%20rent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20ways%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20other%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EGiving%20up%20your%20weekly%20bakery%20treat%20probably%20isn't%20going%20to%20make%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20how%20much%20money%20you%20have%20left%20over%20each%20month%2C%20but%20looking%20at%20larger%2C%20regular%20costs%20can.%20Shopping%20at%20a%20less%20expensive%20grocery%20store%2C%20for%20example%2C%20or%20using%20a%20gym%20with%20a%20cheaper%20membership%20could%20give%20you%20a%20bit%20more%20breathing%20room%20in%20your%20monthly%20budget.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncrease%20your%20income%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Obviously%2C%20this%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20Ways%20to%20increase%20your%20income%20include%20finding%20a%20higher-paying%20job%2C%20asking%20for%20a%20raise%2C%20or%20taking%20on%20a%20side%20hustle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Frenting-vs-buying-house-pros-cons%5C%22%3Erenting%20vs.%20buying%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThough%20renting%20is%20often%20more%20affordable%20than%20owning%20a%20home%2C%20there%20are%20situations%20where%20buying%20could%20make%20more%20sense.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgage-calculator%5C%22%3Emortgage%20calculator%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20help%20you%20determine%20whether%20homeownership%20is%20affordable%20for%20you.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EHow%20much%20rent%20c