20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card%20is%20worth%20considering%20if%20you%20fly%20Southwest%2C%20even%20occasionally.%20This%20card%20strikes%20the%20best%20balance%20between%20valuable%20benefits%20and%20a%20moderate%20annual%20fee%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20can%20score%20an%20incredible%20welcome%20offer%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why%20the%20Southwest%20Premier%20card%20is%20worth%20your%20consideration%2C%20and%20what%20you%20can%20get%20with%20this%20card%20in%20your%20wallet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESouthwest%20Premier%20Card%20Overview%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card%20is%20the%20middle%20child%20of%20Chase's%20three%20Southwest%20consumer%20credit%20cards.%20The%20Premier%20card%20comes%20with%20a%20%2499%20annual%20fee%2C%20and%20a%20few%20more%20benefits%20than%20the%20entry-level%20version.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20need%20a%20Southwest%20credit%20card%20to%20get%20free%20checked%20bags%2C%20since%20this%20airline%20is%20generous%20about%20offering%20two%20free%20checked%20bags%20for%20all%20travelers.%20But%20the%20Southwest%20Premier%20has%20many%20other%20benefits%20to%20offset%20its%20annual%20fee%2C%20including%20elevated%20rewards%20on%20Southwest%20flights%2C%20free%20priority%20check-in%20privileges%2C%20and%20discounts%20on%20inflight%20purchases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Rewards%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Premier%20Card%20Rewards%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWelcome%20Bonus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card%20currently%20offers%20new%20cardholders%20the%20chance%20to%20earn%20a%2050%2C000%20bonus%20points%20after%20you%20spend%20%241%2C000%20on%20purchases%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20from%20account%20opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20same%20bonus%20you'll%20find%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-rapid-rewards-plus-credit-card-review%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20comes%20with%20a%20%2469%20annual%20fee%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-rapid-rewards-priority-credit-card-review%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20%2499%20annual%20fee).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20points%20you%20earn%20from%20the%20bonus%20will%20never%20expire%2C%20so%20you%20can%20redeem%20them%20whenever%20travel%20plans%20come%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Earn%20Points%20With%20the%20Southwest%20Premier%20Card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20the%20initial%20welcome%20bonus%2C%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card%20cardholders%C2%A0earn%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E3%20points%20on%20Southwest%20purchases%20(including%20flights%2C%20inflight%20purchases%2C%20Southwest%20gift%20cards%2C%20and%20Southwest%20Vacations%20packages)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20Rapid%20Rewards%20hotel%20and%20car%20rental%20partner%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20local%20transit%20and%20commuting%2C%20including%20rideshare%20(and%20also%20passenger%20trains%2C%20buses%2C%20taxis%2C%20limousines%2C%20rideshare%2C%20ferries%2C%20toll%20bridges%20and%20highways%2C%20and%20parking%20lots%20and%20garages)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20internet%2C%20cable%2C%20phone%20services%2C%20and%20select%20streaming%20(Apple%20Music%2C%20Apple%20TV%2C%20Disney%2B%2C%20ESPN%2B%2C%20Fubo%20TV%2C%20HBO%20Max%2C%20Hulu%2C%20Netflix%2C%20Pandora%2C%20Paramount%2B%2C%20Peacock%2C%20Showtime%2C%20SiriusXM%2C%20Sling%2C%20Spotify%2C%20YouTube%20Premium%2C%20YouTube%20TV%2C%20and%20Vudu)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20point%20per%20dollar%20on%20everything%20else%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-are-points-miles-worth-value%5C%22%3Evalues%20Southwest%20points%20at%201.4%20cents%3C%2Fa%3E%20apiece%2C%20on%20average%2C%20so%20your%20rewards%20can%20add%20up%20quite%20quickly%20if%20you%20frequently%20travel%20and%20pay%20some%20bills%20on%20this%20credit%20card.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Use%20Points%20From%20the%20Southwest%20Premier%20Card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20points%20never%20expire%2C%20so%20you%20can%20wait%20to%20redeem%20your%20points%20for%20flights%20within%20the%20US%20(including%20Hawaii)%2C%20and%20to%20Mexico%2C%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20and%20Central%20America.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-earn-redeem-southwest-points%5C%22%3Eredeem%20Southwest%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20award%20chart%20to%20figure%20out%20or%20blackout%20dates%20to%20work%20around.%20The%20number%20of%20points%20required%20for%20a%20Southwest%20award%20flight%20depends%20on%20the%20price%20of%20a%20paid%20ticket.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20you'll%20get%20the%20lowest%20price%20if%20you%20choose%20the%20lowest-tier%20fares%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BWanna%20Get%20Away%26quot%3B%20fares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooking%20an%20award%20flight%20is%20a%20straightforward%20process%20%E2%80%94%20just%20search%20on%20the%20Southwest%20website%20the%20same%20way%20you%20would%20for%20a%20paid%20ticket.%20You'll%20be%20able%20to%20toggle%20between%20the%20cash%20price%20and%20the%20points%20cost%2C%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20compare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20almost%20always%20get%20the%20best%20value%20by%20using%20your%20points%20for%20Southwest%20flights.%20But%20as%20a%20Southwest%20credit%20cardholder%2C%20you'll%20have%20other%20options%20for%20redeeming%20your%20points.%20The%20More%20Rewards%20program%20allows%20you%20to%20use%20points%20for%20merchandise%2C%20gift%20cards%2C%20car%20rentals%2C%20hotels%2C%20cruises%2C%20and%20experiences.%20The%20value%20per%20point%20varies%20depending%20on%20the%20redemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20you%20can%20now%20redeem%20Southwest%20points%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-use-chase-pay-yourself-back%5C%22%3EChase%20Pay%20Yourself%20Back%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20statement%20credit%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20up%20to%201%20cent%20each.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20your%20points%20to%20offset%20the%20card's%20annual%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Benefits%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Premier%20Card%20Benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card%20comes%20with%20handy%20benefits%20that%20can%20give%20you%20a%20boost%20toward%20elite%20status%20and%20give%20you%20peace%20of%20mind%20when%20you%20travel%20or%20make%20big%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarn%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20is%20widely%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20deals%20in%20travel.%20It%20effectively%20doubles%20the%20value%20of%20your%20points%20(or%20cash)%20when%20flying%20Southwest.%20You%20can%20bring%20a%20travel%20buddy%20for%20free%20%3Cem%3Eevery%20single%20time%20you%20fly%20Southwest%3C%2Fem%3E%20until%20the%20pass%20expires.%20Depending%20on%20how%20often%20you%20fly%20Southwest%2C%20you%20and%20a%20partner%20could%20receive%20hundreds%20(or%20even%20thousands)%20of%20dollars%20from%20this%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlyBird%20Check-In%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20data-analytics-product-name%3D%5C%22Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-id%3D%5C%225e74285fc485402ada36c8e3%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-brand%3D%5C%22Chase%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22aabe4eb060ad715ce5be1f3d33f1e4cb%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22bod