e.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20you%20decide%20on%20this%20card%2C%20be%20sure%20to%20check%20our%20review%20of%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-companion-pass%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20since%20the%20other%20two%20personal%20cards%20come%20with%20an%20identical%20bonus%20but%20lower%20annual%20fees%20(and%20fewer%20benefits).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Rewards%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Priority%20Card%20Rewards%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESouthwest%20Priority%20Card%20Welcome%20Bonus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%20offers%2050%2C000%20bonus%20points%20after%20you%20spend%20%241%2C000%20on%20purchases%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20from%20account%20opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Earn%20Points%20With%20the%20Southwest%20Priority%20Card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%20cardholders%20earn%20Rapid%20Rewards%20points%20at%20the%20following%20rates%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E3%20points%20on%20Southwest%20purchases%20(including%20flights%2C%20inflight%20purchases%2C%20Southwest%20gift%20cards%2C%20and%20Southwest%20Vacations%20packages)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20Rapid%20Rewards%20hotel%20and%20car%20rental%20partner%20purchases%20(see%20the%20full%20list%20%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20local%20transit%20and%20commuting%2C%20including%20rideshare%20(and%20also%20passenger%20trains%2C%20buses%2C%20taxis%2C%20limousines%2C%20rideshare%2C%20ferries%2C%20toll%20bridges%20and%20highways%2C%20and%20parking%20lots%20and%20garages)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20internet%2C%20cable%2C%20phone%20services%2C%20and%20select%20streaming%20(Apple%20Music%2C%20Apple%20TV%2C%20Disney%2B%2C%20ESPN%2B%2C%20Fubo%20TV%2C%20HBO%20Max%2C%20Hulu