ts%20until%20you're%20ready%20to%20travel.%20However%2C%20Southwest%20credit%20card%20holders%20do%20have%20other%20options%20for%20redeeming%20points%20through%20the%20More%20Rewards%20program%2C%20including%20merchandise%2C%20gift%20cards%2C%20car%20rentals%2C%20hotels%2C%20cruises%2C%20and%20experiences.%20The%20value%20you'll%20get%20per%20point%20varies%2C%20but%20these%20redemptions%20usually%20provide%20poor%20value%20compared%20to%20redeeming%20for%20Southwest%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Benefits%20and%20Features%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Priority%20Benefits%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarn%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20Points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20deals%20in%20the%20travel%20world%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20fly%20around%20the%20U.S.%2C%20Mexico%2C%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20and%20Central%20America.%20The%20Companion%20Pass%20allows%20you%20to%20bring%20a%20companion%20on%20any%20paid%20or%20award%20flights%20for%20just%20the%20cost%20of%20taxes%20and%20fees%20(typically%20%245.60%20for%20domestic%20flights).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20use%20your%20Companion%20Pass%20for%20an%20unlimited%20number%20of%20flights%20while%20it's%20valid%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20you%20take%20100%20flights%20a%20year.%20It's%20effectively%20an%20unlimited%20buy-one-get-one%20certificate%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2475%20Annual%20Southwest%20Airlines%20Travel%20Credit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%20has%20a%20%2475%20annual%20travel%20credit%2C%20which%20is%20valid%20for%20any%20Southwest%20purchase%20except%20upgraded%20boarding%20and%20in-flight%20purchases.%20Just%20buy%20a%20Southwest%20ticket%2C%20pay%20with%20the%20Priority%20card%2C%20and%20you'll%20receive%20a%20%2475%20credit%20on%20your%20credit%20card%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20spend%20%2475%20or%20more%20on%20Southwest%20flights%20each%20year%2C%20this%20credit%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20offset%20the%20%24149%20annual%20fee%2C%20effectively%20cutting%20it%20in%20half.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnniversary%20Points%20Bonus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20year%20when%20you%20renew%20your%20card%2C%20you'll%20receive%207%2C500%20points%2C%20which%20are%20worth%20around%20%24105%20in%20Southwest%20airfare.%20That's%20enough%20to%20offset%20much%20of%20the%20%24149%20annual%20fee%20if%20you%20use%20Rapid%20Rewards%20points%20toward%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpgraded%20Boardings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20card%20will%20reimburse%20you%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20four%20upgraded%20boardings%20with%20Southwest%20every%20year.%20This%20benefit%20is%20different%20from%20Southwest%20Early%20Bird%20Check-In%2C%20which%20you%20purchase%20at%20the%20time%20of%20booking%20or%20add%20afterward.%20Upgraded%20boarding%20is%20sold%20at%20the%20gate%20when%20extra%20space%20is%20available%20in%20the%20A1-A15%20boarding%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Southwest%20seating%20is%20famously%20first-come-first-served%2C%20upgraded%20boarding%20can%20be%20a%20great%20way%20to%20avoid%20a%20middle%20seat%20or%20to%20ensure%20you%20and%20your%20travel%20companions%20can%20board%20together.%20This%20normally%20costs%20%2430%20to%20%2480%20per%20flight%2C%20but%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%20will%20reimburse%20you%20for%20the%20first%20four%20upgraded%20boardings%20you%20purchase%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflight%20Purchase%20Discount%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%C2%A0also%20offers%20a%2025%25%20rebate%20on%20inflight%20purchases%20%E2%80%94%20including%20premium%20drinks%2C%20Wi-Fi%2C%20movies%2C%20and%20messaging%20%E2%80%94%20when%20you%20pay%20with%20your%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20get%20a%20free%20checked%20bag%20with%20this%20card.%20But%20you%20don't%20need%20this%20perk%2C%20because%20Southwest%20is%20the%20rare%20airline%20that%20offers%20two%20checked%20bags%20for%20free%20for%20all%20travelers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFast-Track%20to%20Southwest%20A-List%20Elite%20Status%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20aiming%20for%20Southwest's%20A-List%20or%20A-List%20Preferred%20elite%20status%2C%20this%20card%20can%20also%20help%20you%20reach%20the%20next%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpending%20on%20a%20Southwest%20credit%20card%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20earn%20Tier%20Qualifying%20Points%20(TQPs)%20beyond%20flying%20on%20a%20paid%20Southwest%20ticket.%20You'll%20earn%201%2C500%20TQPs%20per%20%245%2C000%20spent%20on%20eligible%20net%20purchases%20on%20your%20Southwest%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECar%20Rental%20Insurance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20use%20your%20card%20to%20pay%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20your%20car%20rental%20and%20decline%20the%20rental%20company's%20collision%20damage%20waiver%2C%20you'll%20get%20coverage%20for%20damage%20due%20to%20collision%20or%20theft%20on%20most%20rental%20cars%20in%20the%20US%20and%20abroad.%20This%20coverage%20is%20secondary%20to%20your%20own%20personal%20policy%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20primary%20car%20rental%20insurance%20overseas%20(or%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20your%20own%20insurance).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurchase%20Protection%20and%20Extended%20Warranty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEligible%20purchases%20made%20with%20your%20card%20can%20be%20covered%20against%20damage%20or%20theft%20for%20120%20days%20with%20the%20card's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fchase-purchase-protection%5C%22%3Epurchase%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20up%20to%20%24500%20per%20claim%20and%20up%20to%20%2450%2C000%20per%20account.%20And%20if%20the%20item%20you%20purchase%20has%20an%20eligible%20manufacturer's%20warranty%20of%20three%20years%20or%20less%2C%20paying%20with%20this%20card%20will%20grant%20you%20an%20additional%20year%20of%20warranty%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELost%20Luggage%20Reimbursement%20and%20Baggage%20Delay%20Insurance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20luggage%20is%20also%20covered%20under%20Southwest's%20card%20insurance%20when%20you%20travel%3A%20If%20you%20use%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%20card%20to%20pay%20for%20your%20flights%20and%20your%20bags%20are%20delayed%20over%20six%20hours%2C%20you'll%20be%20reimbursed%20for%20necessities%20(up%20to%20%24100%20a%20day%20for%20three%20days).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20your%20bags%20are%20lost%20or%20damaged%2C%20you're%20covered%20for%20up%20to%20%243%2C000%20per%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Travel%20Protections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20approved%20for%20the%20Visa%20Signature%20version%20of%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%2C%20you'll%20get%20access%20to%20travel%20and%20emergency%20assistance%20services%2C%20which%20can%20help%20arrange%20things%20like%20medical%20and%20legal%20referrals%20when%20you're%20away%20from%20home.%20Just%20be%20aware%20you're%20responsible%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20any%20services%20arranged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20cardholders%20are%20eligible%20for%20travel%20accident%20insurance%2C%20which%20covers%20accidental%20death%20or%20dismemberment%20when%20you%20use%20your%20card%20to%20pay%20for%20your%20air%2C%20bus%2C%20train%2C%20or%20cruise%20transportation.%20Visa%20Signature%20cardholders%20get%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000%20in%20coverage%2C%20and%20Visa%20Platinum%20members%20get%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20get%20access%20to%20a%20roadside%20dispatch%20hotline%2C%20which%20can%20arrange%20services%20like%20towing%20and%20jumpstarts%20when%20you're%20on%20the%20road.%20Again%2C%20you'll%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20actual%20cost%20of%20the%20service%2C%20which%20gets%20billed%20to%20your%20card.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFree%20DoorDash%20DashPass%20Subscription%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20December%2031%2C%202024%2C%20you%20can%20activate%20a%20complimentary%20DoorDash%20DashPass%20subscription%20for%2012%20months%2C%20which%20gets%20you%20no%20delivery%20fees%20and%20reduced%20service%20fees%20when%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fchase-co-branded-cards-free-doordash-dashpass-membership-2022-8%5C%22%3Eorder%20from%20DoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Caviar%20delivery%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Annual%20Fee%20and%20Other%20Costs%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Priority%20Card%20Annual%20Fee%20and%20Other%20Costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%20has%20a%20%24149%20annual%20fee%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-credit-cards-no-foreign-transaction-fees%5C%22%3Eno%20foreign%20transaction%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20extra%20charges%20when%20you%20travel%20internationally.%20If%20you%20carry%20a%20balance%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%20the%20card%20charges%20a%2021.49%25%20-%2028.49%25%20Variable%20APR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20additional%20charges%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20for%20certain%20situations%2C%20including%20cash%20advances%2C%20balance%20transfers%2C%20late%20payments%2C%20and%20returned%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20the%20Southwest%20Priority%20Card%20Compares%5C%22%3ECompare%20the%20Southwest%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%20is%20the%20oldest%20child%20out%20of%20Southwest's%20three%20personal%20credit%20cards.%20Here's%20how%20it%20stacks%20up%20against%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20and%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card%20vs.%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card%20is%20the%20middle%20child%20of%20the%20credit%20card%20family%2C%20with%20an%20annual%20fee%20of%20%2499.%20Your%20earning%20rate%20is%20also%20comparable%20to%20that%20of%20the%20Priority%20card%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E3%20points%20on%20Southwest%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20Rapid%20Rewards%20hotel%20and%20car%20rental%20partner%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20local%20transit%20and%20commuting%2C%20including%20rideshares%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%20points%20on%20Internet%2C%20cable%2C%20phone%20services%2C%20and%20select%20streaming%20services%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20point%20on%20everything%20else%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20you%20can%20earn%20the%20same%20generous%20welcome%20offer%20as%20the%20Priority%2C%20making%20the%20Premier%20card%20a%20great%20deal%20if%20you%20want%20the%20bonus%20without%20the%20higher%20annual%20fee.%20You'll%20get%20the%2050%2C000%20bonus%20points%20after%20you%20spend%20%241%2C000%20on%20purchases%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20from%20account%20opening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20earn%20slightly%20fewer%20anniversary%20points%20on%20the%20Premier%3A%206%2C000%20Rapid%20Rewards%20points%20every%20year%20when%20you%20renew%20the%20card%2C%20compared%20to%207%2C500%20on%20the%20Priority%20card.%20Instead%20of%20four%20Upgraded%20Boarding%20credits%20on%20the%20Priority%20card%2C%20you'll%20receive%20two%20complimentary%20EarlyBird%20check-in%20credits%20each%20year%20with%20the%20Premier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20still%20earn%201%2C500%20Tier%20Qualifying%20Points%20toward%20A-List%20status%20for%20every%20%245%2C000%20you%20spend%20with%20no%20limits%2C%20as%20well%20as%2025%25%20back%2