20and%20Vudu)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E1x%20point%20on%20everything%20else%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Use%20Points%20From%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20Card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20has%20an%20expansive%20domestic%20route%20network%20(including%20Hawaii)%20and%20also%20flies%20to%20a%20number%20of%20international%20destinations%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Central%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20doesn't%20publish%20an%20award%20chart%20like%20some%20other%20airlines%20do.%20Instead%2C%20the%20number%20of%20points%20required%20for%20an%20award%20flight%20is%20tied%20to%20the%20price%20of%20a%20paid%20ticket.%20Based%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20points%20and%20miles%20valuations%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20to%20get%20an%20average%20value%20of%201.4%20cents%20per%20Southwest%20point%20when%20you%20redeem%20them%20for%20award%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-earn-redeem-southwest-points%5C%22%3ERedeeming%20Southwest%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20book%20award%20flights%20online%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20once%20you%20log%20into%20your%20Rapid%20Rewards%20account%2C%20search%20for%20flights%20just%20as%20you%20would%20if%20you%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20paid%20ticket.%20The%20website%20allows%20you%20to%20toggle%20between%20the%20cash%20price%20and%20the%20points%20cost%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20compare%20the%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20flying%20Southwest%20right%20now%2C%20there's%20no%20harm%20in%20holding%20on%20to%20your%20points%20until%20you're%20ready%2C%20because%20they'll%20never%20expire.%20However%2C%20Southwest%20credit%20card%20holders%20do%20have%20other%20options%20for%20redeeming%20points%20through%20the%20More%20Rewards%20program%2C%20including%20merchandise%2C%20gift%20cards%2C%20car%20rentals%2C%20hotels%2C%20cruises%2C%20and%20experiences.%20The%20value%20you'll%20get%20per%20point%20varies%2C%20but%20it's%20typically%20much%20lower%20than%20what%20you'd%20get%20if%20you%20redeemed%20for%20Southwest%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Benefits%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20Benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20doesn't%20come%20with%20some%20of%20the%20other%20benefits%20offered%20by%20other%20Southwest%20cards%2C%20such%20as%20elite-qualifying%20points%20or%20travel%20credits.%20But%20you'll%20still%20get%20a%20variety%20of%20travel%20and%20purchase%20protections%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarn%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-companion-pass%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Companion%20Pass%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20deals%20in%20travel%2C%20particularly%20for%20travelers%20who%20book%20a%20lot%20of%20flights%20around%20the%20US%2C%20Mexico%2C%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20and%20Central%20America.%20With%20the%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20you%20can%20bring%20a%20companion%20on%20any%20paid%20or%20award%20flights%20for%20just%20the%20cost%20of%20taxes%20and%20fees%20%E2%80%93%20typically%20%245.60%20one%20way%20on%20most%20domestic%20flights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlyBird%20Check-In%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECardholders%20receive%20two%20EarlyBird%20Check-Ins%20per%20account%20anniversary%20year%2C%20awarded%20as%20a%20statement%20credit%20after%20your%20purchase.%20EarlyBird%20Check-In%20normally%20costs%20%2415%20to%20%2425%20each%20way%2C%20and%20allows%20you%20to%20automatically%20check%20in%20for%20your%20flight%2036%20hours%20prior%20to%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Southwest%20determines%20your%20boarding%20position%20by%20the%20time%20you%20check%20in%2C%20this%20feature%20can%20help%20you%20get%20on%20the%20airplane%20sooner%20and%20have%20a%20better%20opportunity%20to%20select%20your%20desired%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnniversary%20Points%20Bonus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20receive%203%2C000%20Rapid%20Rewards%20points%20yearly%20when%20you%20renew%20your%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card.%20These%20points%20are%20worth%20around%20%2442%20in%20Southwest%20airfare%20based%20on%20our%20valuations%2C%20and%20can%20offset%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20%2469%20annual%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflight%20Purchase%20Discount%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20receive%2025%25%20back%20as%20a%20statement%20credit%20when%20you%20use%20your%20card%20for%20inflight%20purchases%20(drinks%20or%20Wi-Fi).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECar%20Rental%20Insurance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20use%20your%20card%20to%20pay%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20your%20car%20rental%20and%20decline%20the%20rental%20company's%20collision%20damage%20waiver%2C%20you'll%20get%20coverage%20for%20damage%20due%20to%20collision%20or%20theft.%20This%20coverage%20is%20secondary%20to%20your%20own%20personal%20policy%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20primary%20car%20rental%20insurance%20overseas%20(or%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20your%20own%20insurance).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurchase%20Protection%20and%20Extended%20Warranty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20purchases%20made%20with%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20are%20covered%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fchase-purchase-protection%5C%22%3EChase%20purchase%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20120%20days%20against%20damage%20or%20theft%2C%20up%20to%20%24500%20per%20claim%20and%20%2450%2C000%20per%20account.%20You%20can%20also%20save%20money%20because%20the%20card%20extends%20the%20time%20period%20of%20a%20US%20manufacturer's%20warranty%20by%20an%20additional%20year%20on%20eligible%20warranties%20of%20three%20years%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELost%20Luggage%20Reimbursement%20and%20Baggage%20Delay%20Insurance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20use%20your%20card%20to%20pay%20for%20your%20fare%2C%20you%20(and%20your%20immediate%20family)%20are%20covered%20if%20your%20checked%20or%20carry-on%20luggage%20is%20lost%20or%20damaged%20by%20the%20carrier%2C%20up%20to%20%243%2C000%20per%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20your%20bags%20are%20delayed%20by%20six%20hours%20or%20more%2C%20you're%20eligible%20for%20up%20to%20%24300%20in%20reimbursement%20(%24100%20a%20day%20for%20up%20to%20three%20days)%20for%20essential%20items%20like%20toiletries%20and%20clothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETravel%20Protections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20approved%20for%20the%20Visa%20Signature%20version%20of%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%2C%20you'll%20get%20access%20to%20travel%20and%20emergency%20assistance%20services%2C%20which%20can%20help%20arrange%20things%20like%20medical%20and%20legal%20referrals%20when%20you're%20away%20from%20home.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20you're%20responsible%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20any%20services%20arranged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20cardholders%20also%20get%20travel%20accident%20insurance%2C%20which%20covers%20accidental%20death%20or%20dismemberment%20when%20they%20use%20their%20card%20to%20pay%20for%20air%2C%20bus%2C%20train%2C%20or%20cruise%20transportation.%20Visa%20Signature%20cardholders%20get%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000%20in%20coverage%2C%20and%20Visa%20Platinum%20members%20get%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20you'll%20also%20get%20access%20to%20a%20roadside%20dispatch%20hotline%2C%20which%20can%20arrange%20services%20like%20towing%20and%20jumpstarts%20when%20you're%20on%20the%20road.%20Again%2C%20you'll%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20actual%20cost%20of%20the%20service%2C%20which%20gets%20billed%20to%20your%20card.%C2%A0%3