0Credit%20Card%5C%22%3ECompare%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20decide%20if%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20is%20the%20right%20pick%20for%20you%2C%20you%20should%20compare%20it%20to%20the%20other%20credit%20cards%20in%20the%20Southwest%20family%20because%20you%20can%20only%20hold%20one%20Southwest%20personal%20card%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20want%20to%20use%20your%20points%20for%20other%20forms%20of%20travel%2C%20a%20card%20that%20earns%20transferable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fguide-earning-using-chase-ultimate-rewards-points%5C%22%3EChase%20Ultimate%20Rewards%C2%AE%C2%A0points%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20a%20better%20bet%2C%20since%20you%20can%20transfer%20those%20points%20to%20Southwest%20as%20well%20as%20to%20a%20dozen-plus%20other%20airline%20and%20hotel%20partners%20for%20additional%20travel%20flexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card%20vs.%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Premier%20card%20is%20the%20mid-tier%20sibling%20of%20the%20Southwest%20card%20family.%20Cardholders%20earn%20points%20at%20the%20same%20rate%20as%20top-tier%20Priority%20credit%20card%20holders%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E3x%20points%20on%20Southwest%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20points%20on%20Rapid%20Rewards%20hotel%20and%20car%20rental%20partner%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20points%20on%20local%20transit%20and%20commuting%2C%20including%20rideshares%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20points%20on%20Internet%2C%20cable%2C%20phone%20services%2C%20and%20select%20streaming%20services%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1x%20point%20on%20everything%20else%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20you%20can%20earn%20the%20same%20generous%20welcome%20offer%20on%20this%20card%20that%20you%20would%20on%20the%20Plus%3A%2050%2C000%20bonus%2