n%20purchases%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20from%20account%20opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20%2499%2C%20you'll%20get%20many%20of%20the%20same%20benefits%20as%20the%20Performance%20card%20with%20slightly%20lower%20earning%20rates%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E3x%20on%20Southwest%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20on%20Rapid%20Rewards%20hotel%20and%20car%20partners%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20on%20rideshares%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20per%20dollar%20on%20everything%20else%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECardholders%20get%20two%20EarlyBird%20Check-Ins%20per%20year%2C%2025%25%20back%20on%20inflight%20purchases%2C%201%2C500%20tier-qualifying%20points%20toward%20A-List%20elite%20status%20for%20every%20%245%2C000%20spent%20on%20the%20card%2C%20and%20a%20boost%20of%2010%2C000%20Companion%20Pass%20qualifying%20points%20each%20calendar%20year.%20They%20also%20receive%206%2C000%20Rapid%20Rewards%20points%20each%20year%20on%20their%20card%20renewal%20anniversary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-premier-business-card-review%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Premier%20Business%20card%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Using%20the%20Companion%20Pass%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Use%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Companion%20Pass%20holder%2C%20you%20can%20book%20your%20flight%20to%20your%20desired%20destination%20using%20cash%20or%20points.%20Once%20your%20flight%20is%20confirmed%2C%20you%20can%20add%20your%20companion%20for%20the%20same%20flight%20online%2C%20through%20the%20Southwest%20mobile%20app%2C%20or%20by%20calling%20Southwest%20customer%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20limit%20to%20how%20often%20you%20can%20use%20the%20Companion%20Pass%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20you're%20flying%20and%20there's%20at%20least%20one%20spare%20seat%20on%20the%20plane%2C%20you%20can%20book%20it%20for%20your%20travel%20buddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20pass%20if%20you%20choose%20someone%20you%20frequently%20travel%20with%2C%20such%20as%20a%20spouse%2C%20child%2C%20best%20friend%2C%20or%20family%20member.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch3%3EDesignate%20your%20Southwest%20companion%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20start%20scouring%20the%20site%20for%20flights%2C%20you%20must%20first%20register%20your%20designated%20companion%20on%20your%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%2C%20log%20into%20your%20Rapid%20Rewards%20account%20at%20%3Cspan%3ESouthwest%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20click%20Choose%20Your%20Companion%20under%20the%20Snapshot%20tab.%20Enter%20all%20of%20the%20requested%20information%20about%20your%20companion%20until%20the%20process%20is%20complete.%20A%20Companion%20Pass%20member%20kit%20and%20membership%20card%20will%20arrive%20within%2010%20business%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20wait%20for%20your%20Companion%20Pass%20member%20kit%20to%20arrive%20in%20the%20mail%20before%20you%20start%20booking%20tickets.%20In%20fact%2C%20you%20don't%20really%20need%20the%20pass%20itself%20at%20all%3B%20you%20can%20add%20a%20companion%20to%20any%20flight%20you've%20already%20booked%20for%20yourself%20directly%20through%20the%20app%20or%20the%20website%2C%20and%20they%20will%20receive%20a%20confirmation%20number%20and%20boarding%20pass%20just%20like%20any%20other%20passenger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAdd%20your%20companion%20to%20a%20reservation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20your%20flight%20is%20booked%2C%20visit%20the%20My%20Trips%20section%20of%20your%20account.%20Find%20your%20flight%20in%20the%20section%20titled%20%26quot%3BUpcoming%26quot%3B%20and%20click%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BAdd%20Companion%26quot%3B%20link.%20Here%2C%20click%20%26quot%3BContinue%26quot%3B%20to%20proceed%20to%20the%20next%20step%20where%20you%20can%20purchase%20your%20companion%20fare%20and%20review%20the%20information.%20Once%20you%20hit%20the%20%26quot%3BPurchase%26quot%3B%20button%20to%20complete%20your%20booking%20reservation%2C%20you're%20all%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20book%20via%20phone%20and%20notify%20the%20customer%20service%20representative%20that%20you%20will%20be%20using%20a%20Companion%20Pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20change%20your%20designated%20companion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20change%20your%20companion%20up%20to%20three%20times%20each%20calendar%20year.%20If%20you%20choose%20a%20companion%20when%20you%20earn%20the%20pass%20in%202024%2C%20you%20can%20rotate%20through%20four%20total%20different%20companions%20before%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20cannot%20switch%20your%20companion%20online%20yourself%3B%20instead%2C%20you%20need%20to%20speak%20with%20Southwest%20directly%20at%20800-435-9792.%20The%20process%20is%20straightforward%3A%20A%20customer%20representative%20will%20take%20the%20information%20about%20your%20new%20designated%20companion%20and%20make%20the%20switch%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20cannot%20book%20new%20travel%20with%20your%20next%20companion%20until%20all%20travel%20with%20your%20current%20companion%20is%20complete.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you're%20traveling%20to%20New%20York%20with%20your%20sister%20in%20August%2C%20but%20want%20to%20fly%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20with%20your%20spouse%20in%20September%2C%20you%20cannot%20add%20your%20spouse%20as%20your%20companion%20until%20your%20trip%20in%20August%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20use%20points%20and%20need%20to%20cancel%20for%20any%20reason%2C%20all%20of%20your%20points%20will%20be%20restored%20to%20your%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20Is%20the%20Pass%20Worth%3F%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20Worth%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20is%20largely%20a%20domestic%20and%20Caribbean%20airline%2C%20but%20it%20also%20serves%20many%20popular%20destinations%20such%20as%20Mexico%2C%20Aruba%2C%20the%20Bahamas%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20Costa%20Rica.%20The%20value%20you'll%20get%20from%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20depends%20entirely%20on%20how%20often%20you%20and%20your%20travel%20companion%20fly%20Southwest.%20You%20could%20easily%20save%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20with%20this%20perk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20points%20are%20worth%201.4%20cents%20each%20toward%20flights%2C%20on%20average%2C%20based%20on%20Personal%20Finance%20Insider's%20current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-are-points-miles-worth-value%5C%22%3Epoints%20and%20miles%20valuations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20Companion%20Pass%20can%20effectively%20double%20the%20value%20of%20your%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20successfully%20earned%20the%20125%2C000%20points%20necessary%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Companion%20Pass%20(again%2C%20the%20qualification%20is%20135%2C000%20points%2C%20but%20Southwest%20cardholders%20get%20a%2010%2C000-mile%20boost)%2C%20you'll%20have%20enough%20points%20for%20at%20least%20%241%2C750%20in%20Southwest%20flights%20(125%2C000%20points%20x%201.4%20cents%20each).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Companion%20Pass%20allows%20you%20to%20bring%20along%20another%20person%20for%20just%20the%20cost%20of%20taxes%20and%20fees%2C%20meaning%20you%20could%20potentially%20get%20%243%2C500%20in%20flights%20(%241%2C750%20x%202)%20just%20from%20the%20points%20you%20earned%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Companion%20Pass%20Frequently%20Asked%20Questions%20(FAQ)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20travel%20benefits%20in%20the%20industry.%20If%20you%20hold%20a%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20you%20can%20bring%20one%20designated%20travel%20companion%20on%20any%20Southwest%20flight%20you%20take%20for%20just%20the%20cost%20of%20taxes%20and%20fees%2C%20as%20long%20as%20there's%20at%20least%20one%20extra%20seat%20on%20the%20plane.%20The%20Companion%20Pass%20works%20on%20both%20paid%20flights%20and%20award%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20Southwest%20buddy%20passes%20free%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20companion%20fares%20are%20almost%20free%20%E2%80%94%20you'll%20only%20pay%20for%20any%20associated%20taxes%20and%20fees%2C%20which%20are%20often%20as%20low%C2%A0%20as%20%245.60%20on%20most%20domestic%20one-way%20direct%20flights.%20Taxes%20and%20fees%20must%20be%20paid%20in%20cash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20can%20I%20tell%20if%20I%20have%20the%20Companion%20Pass%20on%20Southwest%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you%20earn%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20you'll%20see%20a%20banner%20in%20the%20center%20of%20your%20account%20page%20prompting%20you%20to%20designate%20a%20travel%20companion.%20Once%20you%20do%20so%2C%20you'll%20see%20your%20Companion%20Pass%20badge%20and%20companion%20name%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20your%20account%20page.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20get%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20earn%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20by%20earning%20135%2C000%20qualifying%20Rapid%20Rewards%20points%20or%20flying%20100%20one-way%20cash%20flights%20within%20a%20calendar%20year.%20Qualifying%20points%20can%20be%20earned%20through%20Rapid%20Rewards%20credit%20card%20spend%2C%20or%20by%20flying%20with%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20good%20for%20two%20years%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20earn%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20through%20the%20year%20following%20the%20one%20in%20which%20you%20earn%20the%20required%20135%2C000%20points%20or%20complete%20your%20100th%20flight.%20Thus%2C%20you'll%20earn%20the%20Companion%20Pass%20for%20nearly%20two%20full%20years%20if%20you%20can%20complete%20the%20requirements%20in%20January%20each%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20many%20times%20can%20a%20Companion%20Pass%20be%20used%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20is%20unlimited.%20You%20can%20bring%20your%20designated%20companion%20on%20any%20flight%20that%20you%20take%20yourself%2C%20as%20long%20as%20there's%20an%20extra%20seat%20on%20the%20plane.%20You%20can%20even%20use%20the%20Companion%20Pass%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-earn-redeem-southwest-points%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20award%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20booked%20with%20Rapid%20Rewards%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20the%20Companion%20Pass%20only%20for%20domestic%20travel%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Companion%20Pass%20can%20be%20used%20for%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20my%20companion%20fly%20without%20me%20on%20Southwest%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20companion%20cannot%20fly%20on%20a%20companion%20fare%20unless%20you%20are%20on%20all%20of%20the%20same%20flights%2C%20but%20they%20can%20still%20book%20their%20own%20travel%20through%20Southwest%20as%20a%20regular%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-companion-pass%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710362478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F647f51eb9fcce60019359270%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-companion-pass%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20guide%20to%20the%20coveted%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20shows%20you%20how%20to%20bring%20a%20nearly-free%20travel%20companion%20on%20any%20flight%20you%20take%20%E2%80%94%20through%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhostetler%40insider.com%20(Joseph%20Hostetler%2C%20CEPF%2CHarlan%20Vaughn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-companion-pass%22%2C%2