0help%20those%20with%20lower%20incomes%20become%20homeowners%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rocketmortgage.com%2Flearn%2Fone-plus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EONE%2B%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%20allows%20down%20payments%20as%20low%20as%201%25%20with%20no%20mortgage%20insurance%2C%20and%20includes%20a%202%25%20grant%20from%20the%20lender.%20This%20mortgage%20is%20available%20nationwide%2C%20but%20only%20those%20who%20earn%2080%25%20or%20less%20of%20the%20area%20median%20income%20can%20qualify.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rocketcompanies.com%2Fpress-release%2Frocket-mortgage-introduces-purchase-plus-helping-make-the-american-dream-of-homeownership-more-attainable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPurchase%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20program%20offers%20a%20credit%20of%20up%20to%20%247%2C500%20to%20offset%20your%20down%20payment%20and%20closing%20costs.%20This%20program%20is%20only%20available%20in%20specific%20census%20tracts%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20Baltimore%2C%20Chicago%2C%20Detroit%2C%20Memphis%2C%20and%20Philadelphia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERocket%20also%20offers%20Freddie%20Mac's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rocketcompanies.com%2Fpress-release%2Frocket-mortgage-further-expands-affordable-homebuying-options-with-new-borrowsmart-access%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBorrowSmart%20Access%3C%2Fa%3E%20program%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20%243%2C000%20credit%20for%20your%20down%20payment.%20This%20program%20is%20only%20available%20in%20certain%20counties%20within%20the%20following%20metro%20areas%3A%20Atlanta%3B%20Chicago%3B%20Detroit%3B%20Memphis%3B%20Miami%3B%20Philadelphia%3B%20St.%20Louis%3B%20El%20Paso%2C%20Houston%2C%20and%20McAllen%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%3EHistory%20and%20Background%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERocket%20Mortgage%20started%20as%20Rock%20Financial%20in%201985%20as%20a%20mortgage%20broker.%20It%20was%20renamed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fquicken-loans-review%5C%22%3EQuicken%20Loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201999%20after%20being%20purchased%20by%20Intuit%20Inc%2C%20the%20company%20that%20used%20to%20own%20the%20personal%20finance%20software%20Quicken.%20In%202021%2C%20it%20changed%20its%20name%20again%20to%20Rocket%20Mortgage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELoan%20Options%20Available%20with%20Rocket%20Mortgage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EConventional%20Loans%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERocket%20Mortgage%20offers%20multiple%20types%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fconventional-mortgage%5C%22%3Econventional%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20both%20conforming%20and%20jumbo%20loans.%20Its%20jumbo%20loans%20go%20up%20to%20%243%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20a%20conforming%20loan%20with%20this%20lender%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-credit-score-is-needed-to-buy-a-house%5C%22%3Ecredit%20score%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20620%20and%20a%20minimum%20down%20payment%20of%203%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EFHA%20Loans%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20an%20FHA%20loan%20from%20Rocket%20Mortgage%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20580%20credit%20score%20and%20a%20minimum%203.5%25%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-down-payment-for-a-house%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EVA%20Loans%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERocket%20Mortgage%20allows%20slightly%20lower%20credit%20scores%20than%20many%20other%20VA%20lenders.%20To%20get%20a%20VA%20loan%20with%20this%20lender%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20score%20of%20at%20least%20580%20(many%20lenders%20require%20scores%20of%20620%20or%20higher%20on%20these%20loans).%20It%20also%20accepts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fdebt-to-income-ratio%5C%22%3Edebt-to-income%20ratios%3C%2Fa%3E%20up%20to%2060%25%