hree%20countries%E2%80%99%20boundaries%20in%20June%202017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%2073-day%20standoff%2C%20both%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220126065424%2Fhttps%3A%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fdoklam-india-china-withdraw-troops-no-clarity-chinas-road-building-efforts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewithdrew%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20subsequent%20satellite%20imagery%20has%20revealed%20Chinese%20construction%20of%20a%20network%20of%20military%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20end%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20there%20has%20been%20notable%20momentum%20in%20Bhutan%20towards%20the%20finalisation%20of%20its%20border%20negotiations%20with%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20informed%20observers%2C%20Thimpu%E2%80%99s%20proactive%20stance%20is%20driven%20by%20the%20acknowledgment%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle%2F3251394%2Fchinese-village-construction-disputed-zone-outpaces-china-bhutan-border-talks%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esalami%20slicing%E2%80%99%20tactics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20along%20the%20border%20cannot%20be%20effectively%20halted%20due%20to%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20signed%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20to%20expedite%20boundary%20talks%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkuenselonline.com%2Fbhutan-china-sign-mou-to-expedite-boundary-negotiations%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree%20stage%20roadmap%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20After%20the%20delimitation%20of%20the%20border%20on%20maps%2C%20it%20envisages%20joint%20surveys%20for%20demarcating%20the%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%2025%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20round%20of%20boundary%20talks%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20on%20the%20guidelines%20of%20the%20joint%20technical%20team%20that%20would%20delimit%20and%20demarcate%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20with%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi%20said%20that%20Beijing%20was%20ready%20to%20conclude%20the%20process%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchina-bhutan-vow-to-conclude-border-talks-soon-will-have-implications-for-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20soon%20as%20possible%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhutan%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20authorise%20the%20Indian%20military%20road%20until%20the%20border%20with%20China%20is%20conclusively%20settled%20suggests%20that%20Thimphu%20is%20equally%20eager%20to%20conclude%20the%20matter%20without%20jeopardising%20the%20ongoing%20boundary%20negotiations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710354838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F10134907%2F24309575841_545d70a37a_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-pm-india-vist-china-border-talks-shadow%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20proposed%20connecting%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20with%20a%20motorable%20road%20through%20Bhutan.%20But%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20Bhutan's%20government%20is%20not%20keen%20on%20the%20proposal%20until%20its%20border%20with%20China%20is%20demarcated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-pm-india-vist-china-border-talks-shadow%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Breaks%20New%20Ground%20In%20Bihar%2C%20Goes%20One%20Up%20On%20Nitish%20Kumar%20In%20Seat%20Share%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20--%20long%20used%20to%20playing%20the%20supporting%20role%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20Bihar%20--%C2%A0%20has%20taken%20the%20lead%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20will%20spearhead%20the%20NDA%20attack%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20party%20will%20contest%2017%20of%20the%20state's%2040%20seats%2C%20under%20a%20formula%20that%20was%20finalised%20today%20after%20the%20impasse%20with%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20faction%20of%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20was%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20will%20field%20candidates%20on%2016%20seats%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20LJP%20will%20contest%20on%20five%20seats%2C%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%20and%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%20will%20contest%20on%20one%20seat%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan's%20deal%20with%20the%20BJP%20came%20after%20a%20long%20impasse%20that%20was%20followed%20by%20claims%20that%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20has%20been%20sending%20it%20feelers.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20apparently%20offered%20him%20just%20six%20seats%20--%20to%20be%20split%20with%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras%20--%20sources%20said%20the%20Opposition%20had%20offered%20LJP%20eight%20seats%2C%20all%20six%20it%20won%20in%202019%20and%20two%20more%20in%20neighbouring%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20bonus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan%2C%20who%20recently%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3BEvery%20Party%2C%20Every%20Coalition%20Wants%20Me%20To%20Be%20On%20Its%20Side%2C%26quot%3B%20settled%20for%20five%20seats%20today.%20But%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20after%20the%20meeting%20that%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras%20would%20not%20be%20given%20any%20seat%20from%20his%20quota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20sealing%20the%20deal%20is%20a%20huge%20plus%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20from%20a%20position%20of%20isolation%20imposed%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20defection%20to%20the%C2%A0%20Grand%20Alliance%2C%20has%20suddenly%20found%20itself%20rich%20with%20his%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20party%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20was%20second%20to%20none%20--%20the%20one%20extra%20seat%20marking%20it%20as%20the%20alpha%20in%20the%20alliance.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20JDU%2C%20after%20a%20silent%20and%20bitter%20face-off%2C%20had%20decided%20on%20a%2050%3A50%20formula%20and%20contested%20on%20an%20equal%20number%20of%20seats.%20The%20division%20was%2017%20seats%20each%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20Mr%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20and%20six%20for%20Lok%20Janashakti%20Party%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20father%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20had%20won%2039%20of%20the%2040%20seats%20--%20only%20one%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710354720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fk41huekk_nitish-kumar-amit-shah-pti-_625x300_31_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-breaks-new-ground-in-bihar-goes-one-up-on-nitish-kumar-in-seat-share-5233596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22he%20BJP%20--%20long%20used%20to%20playing%20the%20supporting%20role%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20Bihar%20--%20has%20taken%20the%20lead%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20will%20spearhead%20the%20NDA%20attack%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-breaks-new-ground-in-bihar-goes-one-up-on-nitish-kumar-in-seat-share-5233596%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-breaks-new-ground-in-bihar-goes-one-up-on-nitish-kumar-in-seat-share-5233596%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-breaks-new-ground-in-bihar-goes-one-up-on-nitish-kumar-in-seat-share-5233596%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20is%20About%20Truth%2C%20the%20Environment%20and%20Democracy%2C%20Says%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20on%20Day%208%20of%20His%20Climate%20Fast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13231912%2FWangchuk-Sonam.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3EClimate%20activist%20and%20innovator%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20is%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98climate%20fast%E2%80%99%20at%20Leh%20in%20Ladakh.%20The%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20winner%20of%202017%20is%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fast%20unto%20death%20%E2%80%93%20to%20demand%20special%20status%20and%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20virtual%20press%20conference%20from%20his%20protest%20site%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%2013)%2C%20Wangchuk%20highlighted%20why%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20(which%20gives%20states%20in%20hilly%20regions%20with%20a%20significant%20tribal%20population%20special%20administrative%20powers)%20in%20and%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%20is%20crucial%20for%20its%20ecology%2C%20environment%20and%20indigenous%20peoples.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20specific%20questions%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%20that%20the%20climate%20fast%20is%20about%20giving%20rights%20to%20local%20indigenous%20peoples%20in%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20administration%20because%20they%20will%20be%20more%20concerned%20about%20the%20next%20generation%20than%20a%20three-year%20term%20bureaucrat%20who%20has%20no%20idea%20about%20its%20distinct%20topography%2C%20environment%2C%20culture%20and%20linguistics%20would%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMaterial%20development%E2%80%9D%20that%20is%20limitless%20and%20disregards%20natural%20resources%20and%20indigenous%20people%2C%20wildlife%2C%20flora%20and%20fauna%20is%20not%20development%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20also%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20certain%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20lose%20its%20votes%20and%20seat%20in%20Ladakh%20because%20people%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20party%20that%20went%20back%20on%20its%20promises%20to%20implement%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20twice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20innovator%20of%20ice%20stupa%20fame%20appealed%20to%20people%20across%20the%20country%20to%20join%20him%20on%20one%20day%20of%20his%2021-day%20fast%3A%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20citizens%20are%20responding%3A%20many%20plan%20to%20come%20together%20in%20silent%20gatherings%20to%20take%20the%20fast%20on%20Sunday%20and%20show%20solidarity%20with%20Ladakh%2C%20its%20people%20and%20its%20environment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%20truth%2C%20environment%2C%20democracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20virtual%20press%20conference%20conducted%20by%20the%20environmental%20group%20Friends%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20Friends%20of%20Nature%20(FOLFON%2C%20which%20has%20been%20banded%20together%20to%20spread%20the%20word%20of%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20climate%20fast)%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Wangchuk%20first%20gave%20an%20introduction%20to%20his%20ongoing%2021-day%20climate%20fast%20at%20Leh%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20is%20day%20eight%20of%20his%20fast%20and%20he%20is%20surviving%20only%20on%20water%20and%20salt%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSAVELADAKH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SAVELADAKH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSAVEHIMALAYAS%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SAVEHIMALAYAS%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnSonam%20Wangchuk%20appeals%20to%20the%20world%20to%20live%20simply%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cnstarts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FClimateFast%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ClimateFast%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2021%20days%20(extendable%20till%20death)%3Cbr%3E%5CnPlease%20watch%20full%20video%20in%20English%20here%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXHkcIdQQ7b%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXHkcIdQQ7b%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FILiveSimply%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ILiveSimply%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMissionLiFE%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MissionLiFE%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FClimateActionNow%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ClimateActionNow%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKQi5EMro9X%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKQi5EMro9X%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20(%40Wangchuk66)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWangchuk66%2Fstatus%2F1765430525467230455%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20indefinite%20fast%20or%20fast%20unto%20death%2C%20but%20we%20are%20doing%20it%20in%20cycles%20of%2021%20days%20or%20as%20necessary%20because%2021%20days%20is%20the%20longest%20fast%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20kept%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20struggle%20and%20we%20are%20total%20followers%20of%20his%20fast%20of%20peaceful%20expression%20and%20therefore%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20great%20to%20follow%20that%20and%20make%20it%20multiples%20of%20his%20longest%20fast%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20very%20much%20hope%20though%20that%20there%20will%20be%20good%20sense%20prevailing%20on%20either%20side%20and%20everything%20will%20be%20resolved%20sooner%20than%20that.%20But%20if%20not%20we%20are%20very%20much%20prepared%20for%20longer%20durations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20this%20fast%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20truth%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20%5Bthe%5D%20environment%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20when%20Ladakh%20was%20with%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20some%2070%20years%2C%20its%20people%20have%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20entity%20of%20their%20own%2C%20because%20it%20had%20always%20been%20an%20independent%20kingdom%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20like%20Sikkim%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20Tibet%2C%20said%20Wangchuk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20because%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20topography%2C%20environment%2C%20culture%20and%20linguistics%20have%20all%20been%20very%20different%20not%20just%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20India%2C%20but%20the%20world%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Ladakh%20received%20the%20tag%20of%20a%20Union%20territory%20(UT)%20in%202019%20(%E2%80%9Cmuch%20to%20all%20our%20surprise%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20words)%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20were%20very%20grateful%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%20But%20their%20%E2%80%9Cexpectation%20and%20demand%E2%80%9D%20had%20always%20been%20that%20they%20have%20a%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20means%20the%20democratic%20representation%20of%20people%20in%20an%20assembly%20which%20will%20then%20make%20laws%20and%20policies%20to%20manage%20the%20fragile%20ecosystems%20of%20these%20mountains%E2%80%9D%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20thing%20was%20about%20the%20safeguards%20of%20this%20especially%20fragile%20zone%2C%20and%20Article%20370%20provided%20that%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20were%20okay%20with%20%5BArticle%5D%20370%20going%20because%20only%20that%20could%20allow%20Ladakh%20to%20be%20a%20separate%20entity.%20We%20were%20okay%20about%20that%20for%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%A6%20of%20course%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20different%20case%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%E2%80%9CNatural%20no-brainer%E2%80%9D%20but%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deliver%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakh%20expected%20that%20its%20safeguards%20would%20come%20from%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20the%20climate%20activist%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20this%20%5Bschedule%5D%20is%20tailor-made%20for%20hilly%20regions%20with%20distinct%20indigenous%20tribal%20communities.%20And%20normally%2C%2050%25%20tribal%20population%20is%20enough%20to%20qualify%20for%20that%2C%20but%20Ladakh%20has%2097%25.%20So%20we%20were%20hands-down%20qualified%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20commented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20had%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20government%20that%20was%20kind%20enough%20to%20make%20Ladakh%20a%20UT%20would%20also%20give%20us%20that.%20It%20was%20a%20natural%20no-brainer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20itself%20assured%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20again%20and%20again%20that%20this%20safeguard%20would%20be%20given%20to%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20they%20spoke%20in%20large%20gatherings%20about%20this%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-roots-of-discontent-in-ladakh%5C%22%3EThe%20Roots%20of%20Discontent%20in%20Ladakh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20even%20kept%20it%20in%20its%202019%20election%20manifesto%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20in%20fact%20one%20of%20the%20top%20three%20promises%20they%20made.%20(Behind%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20seat%20hung%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20manifesto%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20promised%20to%20implement%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20and%20the%20climate%20activist%20also%20pointed%20to%20it%20in%20between%20his%20address).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20people%20voted%20%E2%80%9Cheavily%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20party%20won%20from%20Ladakh.%20But%20the%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20keep%20their%20promise%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20months%2C%20they%20went%20silent.%20They%20were%20even%20upset%20when%20we%20reminded%20them%20of%20this%20promise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20even%20took%20police%20action%20against%20anybody%20who%20uttered%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9CSixth%20Schedule%E2%80%9D%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20So%20in%202020%2C%20Ladakhis%20decided%20to%20boycott%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20Hill%20Council%20of%20Leh%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20present%20government%20sent%20a%20special%20airplane%20to%20Leh%2C%20took%20Ladakhi%20leaders%20to%20Delhi%20and%20appealed%20to%20them%20to%20let%20the%20election%20proceed.%20The%20government%20promised%20they%20would%20%E2%80%9Csolve%20everything%E2%80%9D%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20tribal%20indigenous%20leaders%20and%20people%20are%20very%20trusting%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20said.%20So%20once%20again%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%9Cvoted%20heavily%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20they%20formed%20the%20government%20for%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Council.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20elections%20were%20thus%20won%20on%20this%20promise%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20Wangchuk%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20four%20years%20later%2C%20nothing%20has%20happened%2C%20he%20added.%20The%20home%20ministry%20kept%20%E2%80%9Cdilly-dallying%E2%80%9D%2C%20not%20taking%20decisions%2C%20giving%20several%20excuses%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Climate%20fast%20is%20now%20our%20only%20resort%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%20on%20March%204%2C%20they%20outright%20denied%20any%20possibility%20%5Bof%20this%5D%20and%20said%20that%20we%20cannot%20give%20you%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20said.%20A%20UT%20with%20legislature%20or%20statehood%20is%20also%20not%20possible%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakhi%20people%2C%20therefore%2C%20%E2%80%9Care%20very%20hurt%E2%80%9D%20and%20our%20%E2%80%9Conly%20resort%E2%80%9D%20is%20to%20start%20a%20movement%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20that%20not%20only%20people%20in%20Ladakh%20but%20all%20over%20the%20nation%20join%20us%20in%20the%20support%20and%20defence%20of%20truth%20and%20justice%20%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20Ladakh.%20When%20somebody%20makes%20a%20promise%2C%20they%20must%20keep%20it%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20giving%20a%20cheque%20which%20says%20Sixth%20Schedule%20and%20then%20you%20take%20it%20and%20it%20bounces.%20That%20should%20not%20be%20acceptable.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20should%20be%20punishable.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20are%20on%20a%20fast.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221007%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809.png%201007w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809-300x130.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695567%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22435%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThousands%20of%20protesters%20rallied%20in%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20districts%20of%20Ladakh%20on%20Saturday%2C%20February%203%2C%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20constitutional%20changes%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%20Photo%3A%20By%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20and%20more%20people%20are%20joining%20the%20fast%20in%20different%20days%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%2C%20showing%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20site%20sitting%20with%20him%20via%20his%20phone%20camera.%20Around%201%2C000%20people%20have%20joined%20him%20for%20the%20fast%20on%20March%2013%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20resentment%20among%20people%2C%20but%20we%20hope%20that%20this%20shows%20the%20central%20%5BUnion%5D%20government%20how%20serious%20the%20matter%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20struggle%20will%20take%20long%2C%20but%20we%20are%20ready%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20commented%20later%2C%20in%20reply%20to%20other%20questions%20posed%20by%20activists%20and%20members%20of%20the%20media%20during%20the%20virtual%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Csurprised%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20paying%20attention%20to%20their%20protest%20in%20such%20a%20sensitive%20region%2C%20which%20is%20surrounded%20by%20international%20borders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakhis%20have%20supported%20the%20Indian%20army%2C%20shoulder-to-shoulder%2C%20on%20every%20occasion%20across%20decades%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5Bthe%20government%5D%20will%20lose%20a%20great%20friend%20if%20they%20keep%20treating%20Ladakh%20this%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20Ladakhis%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20passionate%20about%20risking%20our%20lives%20to%20help%2C%20if%20they%20feel%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20protecting%20them%20in%20any%20way.%20It%20would%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebadkismati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bbad%20luck%5D%20if%20that%20happens.%20And%20the%20current%20ruling%20party%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20this%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLadakhis%20have%20always%20been%20with%20the%20country%20but%20if%20this%20continues%2C%20people%20will%20be%20very%20confused%20about%20what%20to%20do.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20is%20important%20that%20the%20government%20not%20take%20this%20lightly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20regions%2C%20religions%20and%20political%20parties%20in%20Ladakh%20are%20with%20this%20movement%3B%20even%20the%20BJP%20was%2C%20because%20they%20did%20include%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20in%20their%20manifesto.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20different%20matter%20that%20now%20they%20are%20not%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%20in%20response%20to%20questions%20by%20other%20media%20houses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20called%20on%20people%20from%20across%20India%20to%20join%20this%20%E2%80%9Cstruggle%20for%20truth%2C%20struggle%20for%20protection%20of%20fragile%20environment%20and%20struggle%20for%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20innovator%20who%20won%20laurels%20for%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsci-tech%2Fenergy-and-environment%2Fthe-ice-stupa-man%2Farticle21250832.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eice%20stupas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20enormous%20%E2%80%98stupas%E2%80%99%20or%20blocks%20of%20ice%20constructed%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20melts%20slower%20than%20usual%20and%20supplies%20villages%20in%20Ladakh%20with%20a%20constant%20water%20supply%20%E2%80%93%20has%20called%20on%20people%20across%20the%20country%20to%20join%20him%20on%20his%20climate%20fast%20for%20a%20single%20day%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017)%20%E2%80%93%20to%20show%20their%20solidarity%20and%20support%20for%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20activists%20and%20environmentalists%20across%20the%20country%20are%20responding.%20People%20and%20organizations%20across%20several%20cities%20and%20towns%20in%20India%20have%20formed%20groups%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20climate%20fast%2C%20and%20have%20pledged%20to%20fast%20on%20March%2017%20to%20show%20support%20for%20Ladakh%20and%20its%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFOLFON%20founder%20Dilip%20Jain%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20his%20organisation%20has%2020%20active%20chapters.%20These%20include%20activists%20and%20groups%20across%20several%20states%20including%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3B%20and%20city%20chapters%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolhapur%2C%20Pune%20and%20Nagpur%20in%20Maharashtra%3B%20Coimbatore%20and%20Chennai%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3B%20Bengaluru%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Hyderabad%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13232605%2FTso-Moriri-1024x600.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13232605%2FTso-Moriri-1