C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20bulls%20in%20this%20China%20shop%20%E2%80%A6%20If%20it%20is%20just%20like%20this%2C%20then%20it%20is%20open%20to%20all%20industrial%20lobbies%20%5Band%5D%20mining%20lobbies%20to%20come%20and%20exploit%20this%2C%20blindly%2C%20blatantly%2C%20like%20it%20has%20happened%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%20And%20we%20can%20see%20the%20impacts%20of%20that%2C%20from%20Himachal%20to%20Uttarakhand%20to%20Sikkim.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20this%20to%20be%20repeated%20in%20Ladakh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9Clike%20putting%20a%20wall%20around%20Ladakh%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20people%20say%20there%20will%20be%20no%20development%2C%20you%20want%20industries%20for%20jobs%20and%20so%20on.%20Jobs%20and%20industries%20can%20still%20come%3B%20but%20only%20with%20consultations%20with%20the%20local%20and%20indigenous%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20all%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20does%20is%20it%20forms%20autonomous%20councils%2C%20like%20microassemblies%2C%20where%20indigenous%20people%20send%20their%20chosen%20elected%20representatives.%20And%20they%20make%20the%20laws%20and%20policies%20for%20these%20fragile%20hills.%20So%20they%20can%20decide%20that%20certain%20industries%20are%20positive%20and%20others%20are%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20one%20entity%20will%20decide%20and%20it%20will%20not%20be%20in%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20giving%20rights%20to%20the%20local%20indigenous%20people%20%E2%80%93%20because%20they%20will%20be%20concerned%20about%20the%20next%20generation%2C%20unlike%20a%20three-year%20term%20bureaucrat%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%2C%20in%20response%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20question%20about%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20ecology%2C%20environment%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20if%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20is%20not%20implemented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocal%2C%20indigenous%20people%20will%20be%20good%20stewards%20of%20the%20environment%20and%20take%20good%20care%20of%20it%2C%20as%20they%20always%20have%2C%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20virtual%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20applies%20to%20the%20assembly%3A%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20operates%20at%20the%20district%20or%20grassroots%20level%2C%20while%20statehood%20operates%20at%20the%20macro%2C%20state%20level%20because%20the%20funds%20for%20the%20state%20or%20the%20UT%20come%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20right%20now%2C%20this%20is%20decided%20by%20just%20one%20lieutenant%20governor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20the%20region%20will%20never%20take%20decisions%20that%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20is%20important%20for%20the%20environment%20that%20the%20sons%20and%20daughters%20of%20this%20soil%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20decisions%20about%20this%20peculiar%20landscape%20and%20ecosystem%20that%20nobody%20else%20is%20likely%20to%20understand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-citizens-groups-in-ladakh-are-turning-down-the-union-home-ministrys-olive-branch%5C%22%3EWhy%20Citizens%E2%80%99%20Groups%20in%20Ladakh%20Are%20Turning%20Down%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%E2%80%99s%20Olive%20Branch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Material%20development%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20excite%20us%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20two%20days%20ago%2C%20news%20reports%20talked%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclose%20collaboration%E2%80%9D%20being%20worked%20out%20between%20the%20governments%20of%20India%20and%20Iceland%20to%20explore%20more%20sources%20of%20geothermal%20energy%20in%20both%20Ladakh%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeothermal%20energy%20is%20energy%20obtained%20from%20hot%20water%20buried%20deep%20inside%20the%20earth%E2%80%99s%20surface%2C%20which%20can%20generate%20electricity%20from%20heat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWells%20are%20being%20drilled%20as%20part%20of%20the%20endeavours%20to%20develop%20geothermal%20energy%20sources%2C%20Iceland%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%20Bjarni%20Benediktsson%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aninews.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Ficelands-foreign-minister-taps-geothermal-potential-in-ladakh-and-himachal-optimistic-on-direct-air-connectivity20240311183614%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ANI%20on%20March%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeothermal%20energy%20is%20classified%20as%20a%20source%20of%20green%20energy%20because%20it%20is%20renewable%20and%20does%20not%20pollute%20the%20atmosphere%20as%20fossil%20fuels%20do.%20However%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20its%20own%20pitfalls%20in%20many%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20case%20in%20point%20exists%20in%20Ladakh%20itself.%20In%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20Puga%20Valley%2C%20India%20is%20building%20its%20first%20geothermal%20power%20plant%3B%20but%20the%20project%20is%20currently%20stalled%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1059100%2Fin-ladakhs-puga-valley-geothermal-project-holds-promise-but-environmental-concerns-remain%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EScroll%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20because%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Ftopics%2Fengineering%2Fgeothermal-fluid%23definition%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egeothermal%20fluid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20water%20containing%20dissolved%20minerals%20and%20sometimes%20even%20acids%20such%20as%20sulphuric%20and%20hydrochloric%20acid%20%E2%80%93%20leaked%20into%20the%20Puga%20stream%20in%20August%202022%2C%20and%20locals%20complained%20about%20the%20pollution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20are%20these%20the%20kind%20of%20projects%20that%20Ladakhis%20would%20be%20able%20to%20regulate%20if%20they%20had%20the%20power%20to%20do%20so%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeothermal%20and%20solar%20power%20plants%20are%20some%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20benevolent%E2%80%9D%20projects%20being%20slated%20for%20Ladakh%20(though%20even%20some%20of%20these%20have%20problems)%2C%20Wangchuk%20replied%20in%20response%20to%20this%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakhis%20would%20love%20to%20share%20their%20solar%20energy%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20India%2C%20but%20the%20location%20of%20such%20projects%20should%20be%20done%20in%20consultation%20with%20locals%2C%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20a%20ten%20gigawatt%20solar%20energy%20project%20is%20to%20come%20up%20in%20the%20Changthang%20region%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fladakhs-mega-solar-power-project-delayed-to-be-ready-by-2026-101675761954786.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20this%20should%20have%20been%20decided%20with%20the%20consultation%20of%20the%20Changpa%20nomadic%20tribes%2C%20Wangchuk%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20take%20up%20roughly%20150%20square%20kilometres%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20this%20will%20be%20in%20prime%20pastures%20of%20these%20nomadic%20tribes%2C%20who%20produce%20some%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20finest%20pashmina%20%5Bwool%5D%20or%20cashmere%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20%5Bthe%20Changpa%20tribes%5D%20were%20consulted%2C%20maybe%20they%20could%20have%20shown%20better%20places%20that%20do%20them%20less%20harm%2C%20or%20in%20other%20ways%20that%20benefit%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20there%20is%20mining%2C%20of%20uranium%2C%20lithium%20and%20so%20on.%20Maybe%20locals%20can%20give%20solutions%20in%20which%20the%20mining%20can%20be%20conducted%20in%20a%20way%20that%20will%20not%20disable%20them%20for%20life%20for%20%E2%80%9Cso-called%20development%20which%20is%20not%20actually%20development%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20so%20excited%20about%20material%20development%20where%20there%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20what%20you%20want%20and%20disregard%20every%20resource%20that%20nature%20has%2C%20disregard%20human%20indigenous%20populations%2C%20wildlife%2C%20flora%2C%20fauna.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20people%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20current%20government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20BJP%20not%20fulfilling%20its%20promises%20to%20Ladakh%20by%20not%20implementing%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20what%20does%20this%20mean%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMobilising%20peoples%E2%80%99%20movements%20is%20a%20basic%20part%20of%20a%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20replied%20in%20response%20to%20this%20question%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20take%20guns%20or%20anything%2C%20we%20just%20want%20to%20make%20the%20government%20realise%20it%20%5Bour%20problem%5D%20by%20people%20inflicting%20pain%20on%20themselves%2C%20not%20on%20others.%20Not%20taking%20others%20hostage%2C%20but%20keeping%20myself%20hostage%20here%20for%2021%20days%2C%20hungry.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20will%20carry%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20a%20critical%20mass%20of%20people%20that%20will%20be%20dangerous%20for%20the%20government%20after%20a%20point.%20It%20already%20exists%20in%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%A6%20any%20time%20a%20spark%20can%20blow%20it%20up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20government%20in%20a%20democracy%20is%20concerned%20about%20its%20votes%20and%20seats%20%E2%80%A6%20already%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20it%20is%20granted%20that%20they%20have%20lost%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20people%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20votes%20and%20seat%5Bs%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20enough%2C%20one%20seat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20issue%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20what%20kind%20of%20democratic%20system%20we%20are%20going%20to%20have%E2%80%A6we%20want%20enough%20numbers%20of%20people%20to%20join%20us%20and%20this%20is%20the%20only%20way%20the%20government%20will%20move%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20through%20your%20media%2C%20we%20want%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India%20that%20tomorrow%20it%20will%20be%20your%20turn.%20When%20it%20is%20happening%20in%20Ladakh%20we%20have%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20each%20other.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710352836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13231912%2FWangchuk-Sonam.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22h