i%20legislators%20no%20longer%20bothered%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20advantage%20of%20the%20absence%20of%20enough%20tribal%20leaders%2C%20Imphal-based%20legislators%20engaged%20themselves%20in%20vilifying%20certain%20groups%20and%20communities%20as%20the%20source%20of%20all%20problems%20in%20Manipur.%20Every%20lawmaker%20pointed%20to%20the%20illegal%20influx%20from%20Myanmar%20as%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20the%20state%20put%20itself%20on%20an%20equal%20footing%20to%20the%20objectives%20of%20extremist%20elements%20such%20as%20Arambai%20Tenngol%2C%20Meitei%20Leepun%2C%20and%20other%20militant%20groups.%20Such%20offences%20committed%20by%20individuals%20and%20organisations%20receive%20immunity%20against%20legal%20proceedings%20as%20long%20as%20they%20serve%20the%20underlying%20objectives.%20Thus%2C%20the%20session%20was%20silent%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnenow.in%2Fnorth-east-news%2Fmanipur-arms-looted-from-police-station-recovered-in-churachandpur.html%5C%22%3Elooting%20of%206%2C000%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnortheastlivetv.com%2Ftopnews%2Fmanipur-cm-admits-intelligence-failure-during-recent-unrest%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20intelligence%20failure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-violence-governments-response-not-new%5C%22%3Einability%20to%20control%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20these%20proportions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fmeitei-village-surrounded-by-6-kuki-settlements-defies-violence-with-unity-we-grew-up-together%2F1659926%2F%5C%22%3Eattack%20on%20Kuki%20settlements%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fmarginalisation-of-kukis-the-main-reason-behind-manipur-violence%2Farticle67000979.ece%5C%22%3Eresettlement%20and%20rehab