%206-kW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20commonly%20sold%20residential%20rooftop%20solar%20installation%20is%203-kW.%20A%20solar%20kit%20for%20this%20energy%20requirement%20is%20about%20Rs%202%20lakh%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Government%20covers%20Rs%2078%2C000%20as%20a%20subsidy%20(under%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%98PM-Surya%20Ghar%3A%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%E2%80%99).%20The%20consumer%20ends%20up%20paying%20only%20about%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FjClnfkmeWKY%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22New%20Subsidy%20Alert%20Feb%202024%20l%20Prime%20Minister%20Surya%20Ghar%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20this%203-kW%20system%2C%20consumers%20end%20up%20saving%20Rs%203%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20month%20in%20electricity%20bills.%20In%20a%20year%2C%20this%20amounts%20to%20approximately%20Rs%2036%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20a%20year%20in%20electricity%20savings.%20In%20about%20three%20to%20four%20years%2C%20you%20can%20recover%20all%20your%20initial%20investment.%20Following%20this%2C%20this%20solar%20installation%20can%20give%20you%20free%20electricity%20for%20the%20next%2020%20to%2025%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20consumer%20on%20a%20five-year%20EMI%2C%20their%20net%20investment%20comes%20down%20to%20zero%20because%20their%20down%20payment%20gets%20covered%20by%20the%20subsidy%20given%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%20and%20monthly%20EMIs%20are%20covered%20through%20monthly%20electricity%20savings%20achieved%20after%20going%20solar.%20In%20net%20terms%2C%20the%20family%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20arrange%20any%20substantial%20sums.%20We%20call%20this%20the%20zero%20investment%20scheme%20of%20solar%2C%20which%20we%20educate%20the%20consumer%20about%20during%20a%20consultation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fwhgxo61Rm30%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fwhgxo61Rm30%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20family%20(consumer)%20decides%20to%20book%20their%20services%2C%20the%20startup%20draws%20up%20a%20detailed%20technical%20design%2C%20takes%20care%20of%20all%20their%20Government%20permits%2C%20and%20applies%20for%20their%20subsidy.%20After%20the%20consumer%20has%20approved%20the%20final%20design%2C%20they%20pay%20an%20advance%20which%20is%20covered%20by%20the%20subsidy%2C%20and%20then%2C%20the%20company%20delivers%20their%20ready-to-install%20solar%20kit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20ready-to-install%20kit%20includes%20our%20trademark%20Wind%20Pro%20Mount%20elevated%20structures%2C%20which%20are%20also%20known%20as%20module-mounted%20structures.%20Measuring%20about%20six%20feet%20tall%2C%20these%20structures%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20our%20installations%20holding%20up%20the%20panels.%20These%20structures%20are%20very%20sturdy%2C%20come%20with%20a%2010-year%20warranty%2C%20zero-rust%20guarantee%2C%20and%20certification%20from%20IIT-Bombay%20that%20even%20during%20a%20cyclone%20with%20wind%20speeds%20of%20up%20to%20170%20kmph%2C%20nothing%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20rooftop%20solar%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20these%20solar%20installations%20are%20subject%20to%20external%20weather%2C%20elevated%2C%20and%20on%20top%20of%20a%20roof%2C%20and%20subject%20to%20high%20wind%20speed%20pressure.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20durable.%20We%20install%20our%20solar%20kit%20in%20just%20six%20to%20seven%20hours.%20Once%20installed%2C%20the%20customer%20requires%20an%20inspection%20from%20their%20local%20power%20discom.%20Once%20the%20site%20is%20inspected%2C%20their%20final%20bank%20details%20are%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Government%20portal%20and%20the%20subsidy%20comes%20into%20their%20bank%20account%20within%20just%2030%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Nikhil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Government%20recently%20launched%20the%20National%20Portal%20for%20Rooftop%20Solar%20on%20the%20back%20of%20which%20all%20of%20these%20Government%20subsidies%20and%20applications%20are%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20care%20of%20all%20these%20applications%20for%20the%20consumer.%20We%20take%20care%20of%20Government%20permits%2C%20subsidy%20applications%2C%20EMI%20applications%2C%20inspections%2C%20design%2C%20procurement%2C%20etc.%20We%20are%20a%20full-stacked%20brand%20that%20offers%20end-to-end%20solutions%20for%20the%20Indian%20consumer%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20installation%20comes%20the%20most%20important%20part%20%E2%80%94%20after-sale%20service.%20India%20is%20a%20country%20where%20roofs%20are%20subject%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20dust%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20external%20weather%20conditions.%20These%20elements%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20wear%20and%20tear%20on%20rooftop%20solar%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20a%20five-year%20comprehensive%20solar%20care%20plan%20in%20which%20we%20take%20care%20of%20everything%20from%20panel%20deep%20cleaning%20to%20technical%2C%20mechanical%2C%20and%20electrical%20maintenance.%20Once%20installed%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20your%20roof%20and%20solar%20energy%20but%20our%20responsibility.%20As%20a%20policy%2C%20we%20sell%20a%20five-year%20comprehensive%20solar%20care%20plan%20so%20that%20consumers%20can%20enjoy%20the%20benefits%20of%20zero-electricity%20bills%20year%20after%20year.%20Consumers%20can%20renew%20their%20after-sale%20care%20plan%20with%20us%20after%20these%20five%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20rooftop%20solar%20systems%20as%20an%20investment%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20seeing%2020-25%25%20IRR%20(internal%20rate%20of%20return)%20if%20it%20gives%20you%20the%20right%20performance.%20Maintenance%20is%20important%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20realise%20that%2020-25%25%20IRR.%20Every%20month%20or%20three%20months%2C%20a%20trained%20SolarSquare%20technician%20will%20come%20to%20your%20home%2C%20do%20a%20complete%20technical%20check%2C%20electrical%20maintenance%2C%20and%20mechanical%20check%2C%20and%20do%20a%20deep%20cleaning%20of%20the%20solar%20panels%20to%20ensure%20any%20hard%20dust%20or%20bird%20droppings%20are%20removed.%20Following%20this%20check%2C%20you%20will%20see%20a%20spike%20in%20power%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Achieve%20zero%20electricity%20bills%20with%20solar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Rooftop-Solar-1709904626-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344451%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20residential%20solar%20installation%20set%20up%20by%20SolarSquare%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELooking%20to%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20moving%20forward%20for%20companies%20like%20SolarSquare%20will%20be%20managing%20solar%20panels%20that%20reach%20the%20end%20of%20their%20lives.%20These%20discarded%20panels%20are%20often%20left%20strewn%20around%20or%20eventually%20get%20mixed%20up%20with%20domestic%20solid%20waste%20and%20end%20up%20in%20landfills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20International%20Renewable%20Energy%20Agency%2C%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20amounts%20of%20annual%20(solar%20panel)%20waste%20are%20anticipated%20by%20the%20early%202030s%E2%80%9D%20and%20could%20touch%2078%20million%20tonnes%20by%202050.%20Shreya%2C%20however%2C%20believes%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20extend%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20used%20panels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20maintain%20your%20rooftop%20solar%20installation%20well%2C%20it%20can%20last%20up%20to%2030-35%20years.%20So%2C%20once%20a%20consumer%20retires%20their%20solar%20rooftop%20system%2C%20they%20can%20donate%20the%20panels%20to%20non-profits%20working%20for%20a%20worthy%20cause.%20These%20panels%20can%20run%20for%20another%2010%20years%20because%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20maintained%20so%20well.%20These%20solar%20panels%20can%20have%20a%20second-hand%20life%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20does%20admit%20that%20ventures%20like%20SolarSquare%20will%20have%20to%20devise%20comprehensive%20plans%20to%20recycle%20decommissioned%20panels.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20are%20only%20a%20nine-year-old%20company%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20solar%20installations%20that%20have%20reached%20the%20end%20of%20life.%20The%20question%20of%20disposal%20and%20recycling%20is%20important.%20Thankfully%2C%20you%20already%20have%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20that%20can%20recycle%2070%25%20of%20the%20components%20and%20materials%20used%20to%20make%20solar%20panels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Sustainable%20Technologies%20(CST)%2C%20led%20by%20Dr%20Monto%20Mani%20and%20operating%20out%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287506%2Fiisc-bengaluru-reuse-upcycle-old-decommissioned-solar-panels-as-building-material%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Bengaluru%2C%20is%20exploring%20whether%20old%20discarded%20solar%20panels%20can%20be%20upcycled%20as%20a%20building%20material.%20With%20this%2C%20they%20are%20looking%20to%20extend%20the%20panels%E2%80%99%20useful%20life%20by%20a%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20future%20as%20a%20business%2C%20things%20look%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20they%20raised%20Rs%2030%20crore%20in%20their%20Seed%20round.%20During%20their%20Series%20A%20round%20in%20October%202022%2C%20they%20raised%20Rs%20100%20crore.%20%E2%80%9CLower%20Carbon%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20climate%20tech%20funds%2C%20is%20our