0is%20largely%20confined%20to%20rolling%20uplands%2C%20alpine%2C%20subalpine%2C%20glacial%20moraines%20and%20barren%20regions%20of%20the%20Greater%20Himalayas%20and%20some%20parts%20of%20Trans-Himalayas%E2%80%A6%5BIn%20India%5D%20They%20are%20predominantly%20found%20in%20the%20Kargil%20region%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20where%20their%20distribution%20is%20fragmentary%2C%20spread%20across%20Drass%2C%20Suru%20valley%2C%20Shargole%2C%20and%20Zanskar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201237px)%20100vw%2C%201237px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221237%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brown%20Bear%20and%20Snow%20Leopards%20in%20Ladakh%20taken%20by%20a%20Photographer%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582.jpeg%201237w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582-300x187.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582-500x312.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582-768x480.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582-150x94.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343884%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22773%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20people%20at%20Roots%20Ladakh%2C%20Karamjeet%20feels%20that%20he%20owes%20his%20development%20as%20a%20wildlife%20photographer%20to%20Zaheer%20Bagh%2C%20a%20local%20hotelier%20and%20wildlife%20enthusiast%20in%20Kargil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20unwavering%20support%20and%20shared%20passion%20for%20exploration%20have%20made%20him%20a%20constant%20companion%2C%20and%20together%20we%E2%80%99ve%20explored%20various%20parts%20of%20Kargil%20and%20photographed%20different%20species%20of%20mammals%20and%20birds.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20own%20a%20car%20or%20a%20two-wheeler%2C%20so%20he%20would%20often%20take%20me%20to%20places%20that%20were%20too%20far%20out%20to%20be%20reached%20by%20foot.%20I%20would%20also%20like%20to%20mention%20Baseer%20Ul-Haq%20Choudhary%20(IAS)%2C%20the%20former%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC)%20of%20Kargil.%20He%20also%20helped%20and%20encouraged%20me%20a%20lot%20to%20pursue%20my%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20did%20grasp%20the%20basics%20of%20photography%20during%20my%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20studies%2C%20the%20real%20learning%20happened%20in%20the%20natural%20landscape.%20I%20immersed%20myself%20in%20continuous%20experimentation%20with%20any%20camera%20that%20came%20my%20way.%20My%20learning%20process%20involved%20making%20many%20mistakes%20and%20gaining%20a%20variety%20of%20insights%20from%20the%20people%20in%20my%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201170px)%20100vw%2C%201170px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pallas's%20Cat%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671-500x334.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671-768x513.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeet-Singh-4-1709561671-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343886%5C%